1
00:02:45,208 --> 00:02:47,375
参见玉帝
Greetings to your highness

2
00:02:47,542 --> 00:02:50,333
众卿家，大发雷霆，所为何事？
Ministers, why are you so mad?

3
00:02:50,417 --> 00:02:51,625
皇母，你讲先
Queen Mother, you first

4
00:02:51,625 --> 00:02:54,875
玉帝，降龙罗汉将我棵蟠桃树嗰啲仙桃
Your highness, Dragon Fighter Lo Han stole all the peaches…

5
00:02:54,875 --> 00:02:56,792
冚唪唥偷晒去俾牛郎嗰啲牛食呀
…from my peach tree for the Cowherd's cows

6
00:02:56,792 --> 00:02:59,125
唏，点止呀，佢仲串通啲喜鹊
Not only that, he also conspired with Magpie to arrange…

7
00:02:59,125 --> 00:03:01,167
日日搭条鹊桥俾牛郎同织女幽会
…the Cowherd & Spinster Maid rendezvous on the bridge

8
00:03:01,167 --> 00:03:04,167
仆街喇，已经屙咗成窦仔女出嚟啦
Damn it! They've bred lots of children now

9
00:03:04,167 --> 00:03:06,250
玉帝，下面凡间啲男女关系
Your highness, all along I've handled…

10
00:03:06,250 --> 00:03:07,500
应该由我管开嘅
…lovers' relationships in the mortal world

11
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:09,000
点知佢嚟到搞乱档摊
Who would have thought he'd mess it up,

12
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,417
搞到皇帝走去追只鸡
such that the emperor woos a whore,

13
00:03:10,417 --> 00:03:12,958
堂堂一个公主竟然同一个乞儿私奔㖞
and a princess elopes with a beggar

14
00:03:12,958 --> 00:03:14,500
我话佢两句之嘛
I reprimanded him gently,

15
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:17,000
个衰人就偷咗我只哮天犬去炆枝竹喇
he then stole my Heavenly Dog and braised it with bamboo shoots

16
00:03:17,083 --> 00:03:18,625
你系边鬼个呀？
Now who might you be?

17
00:03:18,625 --> 00:03:20,333
在下二郎神呀
I'm God No. 2

18
00:03:20,333 --> 00:03:23,083
玉帝，我只眼都系俾个衰人笃盲埋㗎
Your highness, my eye was also blinded by that bastard

19
00:03:23,542 --> 00:03:25,708
呢只都系哮天犬嘅老替嚟咋
This is just a substitute for Heavenly Dog

20
00:03:27,083 --> 00:03:29,167
国有国法，天有天条
Law and order must be enforced

21
00:03:29,167 --> 00:03:30,792
呢个降龙目无皇法
This Dragon Fighter is outrageous

22
00:03:30,792 --> 00:03:32,583
我希望玉帝批准我郁佢
I hope your highness permits me to beat him up

23
00:03:32,625 --> 00:03:35,292
嘿，财神你唔驶咁冲动
God of Fortune, stay calm

24
00:03:35,292 --> 00:03:36,667
唏，呢啲算小事呀
These are small matters.

25
00:03:36,667 --> 00:03:38,625
佢挞咗我本生死册改到乱晒坑
He stole my Book of Destiny and messed it up

26
00:03:38,625 --> 00:03:40,167
凡间十八年嚟都未死过人
There hasn't been a death in 18 years

27
00:03:40,167 --> 00:03:41,292
搞到啲忤怍佬无得捞
Those undertakers are out of work,

28
00:03:41,292 --> 00:03:42,833
仲搞咗五六百岁人魔出嚟
and there's a centuries-old man

29
00:03:42,833 --> 00:03:44,167
玉帝，呢坛嘢你搞唔掂佢
Your highness, if you can't control him,

30
00:03:44,167 --> 00:03:45,792
我阎王一于告上九重天
I'll bring this up with the Ninth Heaven

31
00:03:45,792 --> 00:03:46,917
玩大佢为止
and make a great fuss

32
00:03:46,958 --> 00:03:49,333
人嚟，马上同我捉降龙上殿
Guards, summon Dragon Fighter to the palace

33
00:03:49,333 --> 00:03:50,208
系
Yes

34
00:03:54,083 --> 00:03:56,042
喂⋯驶唔驶咁大力呀
Hey… not so hard

35
00:03:56,083 --> 00:03:58,042
瞓紧晏觉㗎嘛，大佬
I'm taking a nap, brother

36
00:03:58,125 --> 00:04:01,208
呀⋯乜咁人齐呀，各位
Hey… everybody is here

37
00:04:01,208 --> 00:04:01,833
咩呀⋯
What?

38
00:04:01,833 --> 00:04:03,458
你边系降龙，你系伏虎之嘛
You're not Dragon Fighter, you're Tiger Fighter

39
00:04:04,125 --> 00:04:06,875
一样啫，降龙伏虎一样之嘛
It's just the same Dragon and Tiger are the same

40
00:04:06,875 --> 00:04:07,417
伏虎
Tiger Fighter

41
00:04:07,417 --> 00:04:08,000
玉帝
Yes, your highness

42
00:04:08,083 --> 00:04:09,833
又唔关你事，你做咩上嚟呀？
It doesn't concern you. Why are you here?

43
00:04:10,042 --> 00:04:12,250
我咪代表降龙嚟同大家道个歉啰
I represent Dragon Fighter to apologize to you all

44
00:04:12,250 --> 00:04:13,500
你咁有义气
You speak so loyally,

45
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:14,708
恐怕你都有份呀
are you also a part of this?

46
00:04:14,708 --> 00:04:16,292
喂，边关我事呢？我⋯
Hey! What has it to do with me? I…

47
00:04:16,292 --> 00:04:19,083
超，神仙大晒咩？
Do you think fairies can get away with everything?

48
00:04:21,917 --> 00:04:23,542
哎，哎呀⋯
Ai! Aiya…

49
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:43,542
伏虎，你硬系多事干嘅
Tiger Fighter, you really are interfering,

50
00:04:43,542 --> 00:04:45,042
不过做兄弟嘅，你都算几够雷
yet you're a loyal friend.

51
00:04:45,042 --> 00:04:45,792
心领嘞
I appreciate it

52
00:04:45,792 --> 00:04:46,667
多谢⋯
Thanks…

53
00:04:46,667 --> 00:04:48,208
喂，家吓咁嘅情况
Hey, as things stand,

54
00:04:48,208 --> 00:04:49,875
求其认句错咪撑啰
just make an apology and leave

55
00:04:50,375 --> 00:04:51,583
认句错就想撑呀？
Do you think you can leave just by saying sorry?

56
00:04:51,583 --> 00:04:53,958
我哋两兄弟讲嘢，几时轮到你插咀呀
Who are you to interrupt our conversation?

57
00:04:53,958 --> 00:04:56,500
你个灶君，逢年尾喺下面揾着数
God of Hearth, each year-end… …you seek advantage in the mortal world,

58
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:59,083
人哋俾唔够你，你就上嚟唱衰人哋呀
and speak ill of those families who gave you less

59
00:04:59,083 --> 00:05:00,375
插佢　　插佢
- Poke him    - Poke him

60
00:05:00,375 --> 00:05:02,458
喂，啱啱插完仲好痛㖞，又插？
Hey! You just did and it still hurts, don't poke again

61
00:05:02,458 --> 00:05:03,667
区区一个罗汉
You, a petty Lo Han,

62
00:05:03,667 --> 00:05:05,000
乜嘢事都要你理啰㖞
poke your nose in everybody's business

63
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,708
岂有此理你话，你偷咗我蟠桃
Outrageous! You better compensate me

64
00:05:06,708 --> 00:05:07,583
你好赔啰㖞幡
for the stolen peaches

65
00:05:07,583 --> 00:05:09,833
皇母，分啲俾人冇乜大不了呀
Queen Mother, what's the big deal to share some to others?

66
00:05:09,875 --> 00:05:10,625
咩呀？
What?

67
00:05:10,625 --> 00:05:12,125
你年年生日吔蟠桃都吔到漏啦
You must get fed up with peaches on your birthday each year

68
00:05:12,125 --> 00:05:12,792
咩呀？
What?

69
00:05:12,792 --> 00:05:13,917
今年转吓口味吔条蕉吖
Why not have a change and eat bananas this year

70
00:05:13,917 --> 00:05:14,542
吓？
What?

71
00:05:16,333 --> 00:05:17,250
咩呀？
What?

72
00:05:17,250 --> 00:05:18,333
条气唔顺当面同我讲
Tell me frankly if you're still angry

73
00:05:18,333 --> 00:05:19,708
唔好揾只狗吠吠拱
Don't have your dog howl for you

74
00:05:19,708 --> 00:05:20,875
咪以为换咗斑点
Don't think just because he has spots

75
00:05:20,875 --> 00:05:22,458
我照噍呀讲你听吖
I can sock all the same, I'm telling you

76
00:05:22,542 --> 00:05:24,250
到边个？
Who's next?

77
00:05:24,292 --> 00:05:25,500
就你啦
You will do

78
00:05:27,250 --> 00:05:28,083
你呢个月老
You Moon Match-maker,

79
00:05:28,083 --> 00:05:30,875
持住有几条红绳就将下面啲凡人玩到谢
you fool humans with several red strings

80
00:05:31,417 --> 00:05:33,375
好似嗰个梁山伯同祝英台咁之嘛
Take for instance the Butterfly Lovers,

81
00:05:33,375 --> 00:05:35,458
你做咩系都唔肯将人绑埋一齐啫
why not tie them together?

82
00:05:35,458 --> 00:05:37,167
搞到人哋撞晒坟呕晒血咁
Instead you brought them a tragic ending,

83
00:05:37,167 --> 00:05:38,875
人哋有咩嘢对你唔住呀
what have they done to you to deserve this?

84
00:05:39,083 --> 00:05:41,083
你老啦，你好退休啦
You're old, you should retire…

85
00:05:41,083 --> 00:05:43,000
唔系啲红绳迟啲实绑到乱晒笼
…before you make a mess Who knows, you may make wacky matches…

86
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,750
就搞到男同男，女同女，再搞落去啦
…say like a man with a man, a woman with a woman,

87
00:05:45,750 --> 00:05:47,792
就人同猪，蟑螂同牛，咁你话嘞
or even a man with a pig, a roach with a cow

88
00:05:47,792 --> 00:05:49,458
最惨就系莲藕同石头　　系呀
- Worst of all would be a lotus root with a rock    - Yes

89
00:05:49,458 --> 00:05:50,875
插佢
Poke him

90
00:05:50,875 --> 00:05:52,583
人哋几廿岁，咪恰得就恰㖞
He's old, spare him

91
00:05:52,583 --> 00:05:53,917
做架梁呀，阎罗王你
King of Hades, are you standing up for him?

92
00:05:53,917 --> 00:05:54,708
插佢
Poke him

93
00:05:55,208 --> 00:05:57,458
唔好吓吓话插，家吓我哋讲道理嘅
Don't keep saying poke, we should be reasonable

94
00:05:57,458 --> 00:05:58,375
你只手⋯
Your hand…

95
00:05:58,375 --> 00:06:00,750
点解下面凡间有个女人生咗十六个女
Why there's a woman in the mortal world who bore 16 daughters…

96
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:03,042
你都唔肯俾个仔人哋，点解？
…and was denied a boy? Why?

97
00:06:03,958 --> 00:06:07,750
搞到个女人终于睇唔开，跳海自尽
Consequently she jumped into the sea to kill herself

98
00:06:08,708 --> 00:06:13,417
落到下面，佢都仲要话人哋系枉死
Even in hell, he accused her of innocent death,

99
00:06:13,917 --> 00:06:15,583
将人扔咗落个油镬嗰度
flung her into a frying pan

100
00:06:15,583 --> 00:06:18,708
炸到好似个咸煎饼咁样
and fried her to a crisp

101
00:06:18,958 --> 00:06:22,375
呀⋯你话，天理何在？
Do you think there's justice?

102
00:06:22,375 --> 00:06:24,458
呀龙⋯降龙⋯
Lung… Dragon Fighter…

103
00:06:24,458 --> 00:06:25,625
晕就得㗎啦
Fainting is no use.

104
00:06:25,625 --> 00:06:28,333
人嘅命运一早已成定数
People's fate is predestined

105
00:06:28,333 --> 00:06:29,542
并无不妥
There's nothing wrong about it

106
00:06:29,542 --> 00:06:31,667
几时轮到你无理取闹呀？
So you shouldn't make trouble here

107
00:06:31,667 --> 00:06:34,125
我哋只系照例执行啫　　玉帝⋯
- We're only carrying out orders    - Your highness…

108
00:06:34,125 --> 00:06:35,125
咩嘢照例执行呀？
Carrying out orders?

109
00:06:35,125 --> 00:06:36,125
边个订嘅例呀？
Who set them?

110
00:06:36,125 --> 00:06:37,875
边个够胆一定话啱㗎？
Who dares to say it must be right?

111
00:06:38,333 --> 00:06:39,875
正所谓天外有天
A saying goes, ‘There are other heavens’

112
00:06:39,875 --> 00:06:41,000
玉帝你订嘅嘢
Your highness, if your rules…

113
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,958
若然被九重天嘅菩萨听到
were known by Bodhisattva in the Ninth Heaven,

114
00:06:42,958 --> 00:06:44,875
怕且觉得白痴兼搞笑咋
she'll think this is a joke of a moron

115
00:06:44,875 --> 00:06:46,167
太过分啦
This is out of line

116
00:06:46,167 --> 00:06:48,250
玉帝，各位仙友
Your highness, fairies,

117
00:06:48,250 --> 00:06:51,208
本人觉得降龙罗汉实在太嚣张啦
reckon Dragon Fighter Lo Han is just too rampant

118
00:06:51,208 --> 00:06:53,042
我财神为咗顾存大局
I think, for everybody's advantage,

119
00:06:53,042 --> 00:06:54,417
请玉帝批准我同佢只揪
please allow me to fight him one on one

120
00:06:54,417 --> 00:07:01,000
哈哈⋯　　收嗲　你收嗲啦
- Haha…    - Shut up! You better shut up

121
00:07:01,167 --> 00:07:02,917
我要同佢只揪　　打死人咩
- I want to fight him one on one    - Don't kill him

122
00:07:02,917 --> 00:07:03,625
我要同佢死过
I'll not show him mercy

123
00:07:03,625 --> 00:07:04,833
我唔会放过你㗎
I won't let you go

124
00:07:04,833 --> 00:07:05,708
吓得我呀
Scare me

125
00:07:05,708 --> 00:07:08,167
听住，就算天条几咁唔啱
Listen! Even if there's a loophole in the laws of Heaven,

126
00:07:08,458 --> 00:07:10,125
总有一条可以定你嘅罪
there must be one that convicts you

127
00:07:10,375 --> 00:07:11,708
押佢两个落去凡间
Escort them to the mortal world

128
00:07:11,708 --> 00:07:13,917
一个做猪一个做狗
and make them a pig and a dog

129
00:07:13,917 --> 00:07:15,917
十世不得轮回
No transmigration for them in 10 lifetimes

130
00:07:16,458 --> 00:07:17,333
咪住先
Wait

131
00:07:17,333 --> 00:07:18,208
咩事呀
What is it?

132
00:07:18,208 --> 00:07:19,458
你话做就做呀
Is your word final?

133
00:07:19,542 --> 00:07:20,625
我话做就做啰
Sure

134
00:07:20,917 --> 00:07:22,875
咁我够话你做蟑螂，一齐呀
I say you'll be a roach, let's go together

135
00:07:22,875 --> 00:07:25,583
哎呀⋯拉佢两个落去
Escort them down

136
00:07:25,583 --> 00:07:26,417
咩呀？
What?

137
00:07:26,417 --> 00:07:27,750
咪住，唔好乱嚟⋯
Wait! Don't…

138
00:08:07,625 --> 00:08:10,000
参见大使
Greetings to Goddess

139
00:08:10,083 --> 00:08:13,833
玉帝，我哋每一位成仙至今
Heavenly Highness, each one of us has been a fairy…

140
00:08:13,917 --> 00:08:16,500
少说亦有一万几千年
…for at least ten of thousands of years

141
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:22,833
世情种种，凡间一切，在我哋嚟讲
Worldly affairs to us…

142
00:08:22,833 --> 00:08:25,750
系遥远而微不足道㗎
…are distant and trivial

143
00:08:26,583 --> 00:08:29,125
今日被降龙罗汉咁闹一闹
The mess Dragon Fighter Lo Han has caused today

144
00:08:29,583 --> 00:08:31,542
或者系一个机缘
might be an opportunity

145
00:08:31,833 --> 00:08:34,417
何不借呢一个机缘嚟了解一下凡人
Why not use it to understand the mortal world?

146
00:08:34,417 --> 00:08:36,417
仲系咪咁愚昧无知
To see if humans are still dumb and ignorant,

147
00:08:36,417 --> 00:08:38,042
抑或有所进步？
or they have progressed?

148
00:08:38,083 --> 00:08:41,042
听观音大使讲嘢，真系听出耳油
Goddess of Mercy speaks well

149
00:08:41,042 --> 00:08:42,083
舒服⋯
What a relief…

150
00:08:42,083 --> 00:08:42,708
大使
Goddess,

151
00:08:42,708 --> 00:08:45,042
呢个小子借住为人间抱不平为借口
this kid offends a superior…

152
00:08:45,042 --> 00:08:46,333
以下犯上啫
…under the pretext of fighting injustice

153
00:08:46,333 --> 00:08:47,917
你唔好乱讲㖞，阎罗王
Stop speaking nonsense, King of Hades

154
00:08:48,208 --> 00:08:49,625
大使自有分数嘅
Matters will be taken care of by the Goddess

155
00:08:49,625 --> 00:08:53,625
降龙，你做咁多嘢，目的何在呀？
Dragon Fighter, what's your purpose of doing this?

156
00:08:54,208 --> 00:08:56,875
我只系想呢班自以为高高在上嘅神仙
I want these fairies to get off their high horses,

157
00:08:57,333 --> 00:09:00,000
能够真真正正咁体验一下啲凡人
and experience the mortal world

158
00:09:00,917 --> 00:09:03,292
因为佢哋一世人只得区区几廿年命
Humans only live for a few decades,

159
00:09:03,292 --> 00:09:05,583
唔好话做错咗一两次错事就翻唔到身
and they shouldn't be condemned for a mistake or two

160
00:09:06,167 --> 00:09:07,625
因为细佬我相信
Because, according to my opinion,

161
00:09:08,458 --> 00:09:10,667
无论佢哋几蠢几无知
regardless of how ignorant and dumb they are,

162
00:09:11,167 --> 00:09:12,833
几恶几抵死都好
how evil and deserving of death,

163
00:09:13,417 --> 00:09:18,292
始终都系⋯即系⋯都系⋯
they are after all… after all…

164
00:09:18,708 --> 00:09:20,833
都系乜嘢呀⋯
After what…

165
00:09:20,833 --> 00:09:21,583
讲啦
Go on

166
00:09:22,125 --> 00:09:24,333
即系⋯个意思即系⋯
I mean… after all…

167
00:09:24,625 --> 00:09:26,583
都系人间有情
Subject to sympathy and love

168
00:09:28,125 --> 00:09:29,708
系咪呀降龙？
Right, Dragon Fighter?

169
00:09:30,375 --> 00:09:32,333
系，就系呢样
Yes, that's it

170
00:09:32,708 --> 00:09:35,125
不如咁啦，亲身落去凡间体验一下
Let's begin with you, going down to the mortal world

171
00:09:35,125 --> 00:09:36,708
由你开始，好唔好呀？
to experience it. Alright?

172
00:09:36,708 --> 00:09:38,625
怕你呀，我正有此意
In fact that's what I intend to do

173
00:09:38,625 --> 00:09:39,875
咁你点证明呀
How are you going to prove it?

174
00:09:39,875 --> 00:09:41,875
我哋已经拣咗三个人版
We've chosen 3 people

175
00:09:41,875 --> 00:09:44,583
呢三个人嘅命运已经注定咗
with predestined fates

176
00:09:44,583 --> 00:09:46,500
一个要做九世乞儿
One will be a beggar for 9 lives

177
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:48,375
一个做九世臭鸡
One a prostitute for 9 lives,

178
00:09:48,375 --> 00:09:50,333
一个系九世恶人
and one a villain for 9 lives

179
00:09:50,333 --> 00:09:51,083
降龙
Dragon Fighter,

180
00:09:51,083 --> 00:09:53,542
如果你能够改变佢哋嘅命运嘅话
if you can change their fates,

181
00:09:53,542 --> 00:09:54,958
咁⋯就算你赢嘞
then you win

182
00:09:54,958 --> 00:09:57,125
你讲得啲神仙咁衰呀，好
Since you despise gods, alright,

183
00:09:57,125 --> 00:09:58,625
你就用凡人嘅身份落去
you'll go as a layman…

184
00:09:58,625 --> 00:09:59,792
唔准用法力
…and not allowed to use magic

185
00:10:00,042 --> 00:10:01,000
唔准带法力？
No magic?

186
00:10:01,125 --> 00:10:03,458
唔用都啱嘅，降龙
That's right, Dragon Fighter

187
00:10:03,667 --> 00:10:05,375
就用你嘅诚意去感化佢哋啦
Use your sincerity to reform them

188
00:10:05,375 --> 00:10:07,792
好，保证唔会令你失望
Okay, I'll not fail you

189
00:10:08,958 --> 00:10:09,917
你等我
Wait for me

190
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,750
我就俾三日时间你
I'll give you 3 days

191
00:10:12,458 --> 00:10:13,542
多谢
Thanks

192
00:10:13,875 --> 00:10:15,375
不过两日半已经够
But two and a half days will do

193
00:10:17,542 --> 00:10:19,292
（南天门）
(Southern Heaven Gate)

194
00:10:19,292 --> 00:10:22,583
唔系事必要你听，但你今日所听嘅一切
You don't have to listen

195
00:10:22,583 --> 00:10:24,000
如果唔照足嚟做
but if you don't act accordingly,

196
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,250
咁你就以后唔驶指意返上天宫嘞
don't expect to return to Heaven

197
00:10:26,250 --> 00:10:28,625
第一，除非你有公文批准
Firstly, unless you have the official permit,

198
00:10:28,625 --> 00:10:30,542
否则唔准擅自进入天宫
you can't enter Heaven

199
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:33,417
第二，你唔可以带任何法力落去
Secondly, you can't take magic powers with you

200
00:10:36,167 --> 00:10:37,667
阿龙⋯龙
Ah Lung… Lung

201
00:10:38,458 --> 00:10:39,500
一路顺风
Bon voyage

202
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:40,500
大家咁话
Same to you

203
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:42,500
好兄弟
Good brothers

204
00:10:42,833 --> 00:10:43,708
仲有乜嘢同我讲
What else do you have for me?

205
00:10:43,708 --> 00:10:44,917
你死梗啦你
You're dead

206
00:10:44,917 --> 00:10:47,083
打你又唔晓打，法术又唔准你用
You can't fight and can't use magic

207
00:10:47,083 --> 00:10:48,583
你落到去仲有唔死咩？
You're bound to die in the mortal world

208
00:10:48,583 --> 00:10:49,208
多谢
Thanks

209
00:10:49,208 --> 00:10:50,167
乜说话呀　　降龙
- Don't mention it    - Dragon Fighter,

210
00:10:50,708 --> 00:10:52,292
你唔会死㗎
you won't die

211
00:10:52,292 --> 00:10:54,208
你响凡间轮回嘅时候
When you re-incarnate in the mortal world,

212
00:10:54,208 --> 00:10:55,750
剩低咗个金身
a golden body has been left behind

213
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:57,917
只要你揾到金身合二为一
Once you find and combine with it,

214
00:10:57,917 --> 00:10:59,833
就可以保住肉身不灭
you can preserve your physical body,

215
00:10:59,833 --> 00:11:01,500
可以穿梭于阴阳间
and transmigrate between the mortal and spiritual worlds

216
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:04,250
亦要靠佢先至可以上番天宫
Besides, with it you can return to Heaven too

217
00:11:04,708 --> 00:11:05,917
实在太好啦
Splendid

218
00:11:06,292 --> 00:11:08,542
今次嘅旅程险阻重重
This journey will be filled with danger

219
00:11:08,542 --> 00:11:10,792
送你一把心想事成扇呀
I'll present you with a Fan of Wishes…

220
00:11:11,375 --> 00:11:13,625
呢把扇每日只可以用三次
…which can only be used 3 times daily

221
00:11:13,625 --> 00:11:15,958
每用一次就会出现裂痕一道
A crack will arise after each use

222
00:11:15,958 --> 00:11:18,042
三次之后要等第二日日出
After 3 times, you'll have to wait till the next day

223
00:11:18,042 --> 00:11:20,583
裂痕自动消失方可再用
when the cracks vanish

224
00:11:21,042 --> 00:11:22,083
一日得三次咁凄凉
A mere 3 times a day, that's pathetic

225
00:11:22,083 --> 00:11:23,667
唔凄凉，好过冇呀
It's better than nothing

226
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:26,333
呢把扇，不能改变生死
This fan can't change life and death

227
00:11:26,333 --> 00:11:28,250
不能改变人心意愿
nor manipulate free will

228
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:30,292
只不过系一种掩眼法
It's just a sleight of hand,

229
00:11:30,292 --> 00:11:33,750
但系凡人往往被迷惑于眼前嘅事物
but laymen are often bewitched by what they see

230
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:36,208
所以都足够你应付有余
So it would serve you well

231
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,167
多谢大使
Thank you, Goddess

232
00:11:38,542 --> 00:11:42,292
凡事小心，切记千奇唔好入邪道
Be careful and don't go astray

233
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:44,958
我会㗎啦
I understand

234
00:11:45,167 --> 00:11:47,250
喂⋯大使明醒你㗎
Hey… Goddess does care much about you

235
00:11:47,250 --> 00:11:48,583
冇呢把扇，你就大剂啦
You'd be in deep shit without this fan

236
00:11:48,667 --> 00:11:50,500
呀⋯　　落去呀
- Yes…    - Go down

237
00:11:51,667 --> 00:11:52,917
喂⋯降龙
Hey… Dragon Fighter

238
00:11:53,458 --> 00:11:56,000
喂，你即系整估啫，佢连把扇都未攞
Hey, you kick him down on purpose

239
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,375
你一脚撑佢落去
He hasn't got the fan yet

240
00:11:57,708 --> 00:11:59,458
玉帝规定呢个时辰㗎㖞
Heavenly Highness has set the deadline

241
00:11:59,542 --> 00:12:01,708
喂，咩嘢玉帝规定啫
Hey, what's Heavenly Highness has ordered?

242
00:12:01,708 --> 00:12:03,542
喂⋯你系咪做嘢㗎真系？
Hey, have you no sense of responsibility?

243
00:12:05,792 --> 00:12:06,958
喂，你喺到做咩？
Hey, what are you doing here?

244
00:12:07,042 --> 00:12:07,792
转更呀
Change of shift

245
00:12:07,792 --> 00:12:09,292
啱啦，同我一齐落去攞把扇俾降龙
Good! Let's go down and pass the fan to Dragon Fighter

246
00:12:09,292 --> 00:12:11,833
喂⋯你冇批文，落到去，你冇法力
Hey… you don't have approval, and you have no magical powers in the mortal world

247
00:12:11,833 --> 00:12:13,292
兼夹见唔到啲凡人㗎
Laymen can't see you

248
00:12:13,292 --> 00:12:15,292
咁所以咪要你同我一齐落去啰
That's why I want you to join me

249
00:12:15,292 --> 00:12:16,458
呢度除咗玉帝之外
Besides Heavenly Highness,

250
00:12:16,458 --> 00:12:18,542
只有你呢个位可以自由出入㗎嘛
only you can come and go as you please

251
00:12:18,917 --> 00:12:20,042
哎呀唔得㗎，犯天条㗎
No, this is against heavenly rules

252
00:12:20,042 --> 00:12:21,375
唏，犯咩天条呀
Forget about the rules.

253
00:12:21,375 --> 00:12:23,542
飞一次咋嘛，好快就返嚟㗎啦，行啦
Just fly once We'll be back soon. Let's go.

254
00:12:23,917 --> 00:12:24,792
咪拘
I'm not going

255
00:12:25,250 --> 00:12:28,042
降龙嗰哮天神犬嗰日，你有份食㖞
You've eaten the Heavenly Dog cooked by Dragon Fighter that day

256
00:12:29,875 --> 00:12:32,250
皇母娘娘个蟠桃你咬咗两啖㖞
You've had 2 bites of the Queen Mother's peaches too

257
00:12:33,792 --> 00:12:37,042
九天玄女两个婢女冲凉嗰日
That day while the Ninth Heaven Fairy's maids were taking a bath,

258
00:12:37,042 --> 00:12:38,333
你个冚家铲
you bastard…

259
00:12:38,833 --> 00:12:39,542
偷睇
…peeped

260
00:12:39,542 --> 00:12:41,458
喂⋯唔好讲，唔好爆出嚟呀
Hey… Stop it! Don't expose it

261
00:12:41,458 --> 00:12:42,625
系咪贱格呢
Creep!

262
00:12:42,625 --> 00:12:44,375
系要爆晒你啲嘢出嚟至肯就范
You won't yield without threats

263
00:12:44,375 --> 00:12:45,292
早去早回啦
Come back early

264
00:12:45,292 --> 00:12:46,167
惊喇咩？
You are sacred, aren't you?

265
00:12:46,375 --> 00:12:48,083
俾人知道唔系几好意思嘅
It's not good to let others know

266
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:53,417
（国清寺）
(Guo Ching Temple)

267
00:12:54,917 --> 00:12:57,667
嗱，左右两边就系十八罗汉
The eighteen Lo Hans are on both sides

268
00:12:57,667 --> 00:13:00,125
降龙伏虎呢，就喺呢一边嚟嘞
Dragon and Tiger Fighters are on this side

269
00:13:00,625 --> 00:13:02,458
至于求子啦㖞
To ask for a son,

270
00:13:02,458 --> 00:13:05,750
咁就梗系要拜观音大使啦
you need to pray to Goddess of Mercy

271
00:13:09,083 --> 00:13:11,333
大慈大悲观世音菩萨
Goddess of Mercy,

272
00:13:11,333 --> 00:13:13,750
求你保佑我可以生番个仔
do bless me with a son

273
00:13:16,167 --> 00:13:19,542
希望大使真系显灵啦，若然唔系
Hope Goddess'll show her power, otherwise…

274
00:13:19,542 --> 00:13:22,417
过埋今年，我就四十㗎啦
…I'll be forty next year

275
00:13:22,417 --> 00:13:24,250
我李茂春任节度使多年
I, Li Mau Cheun, have been honest

276
00:13:24,250 --> 00:13:25,542
自问为官清廉
as an envoy all these years

277
00:13:25,542 --> 00:13:28,333
问心无愧，呢啲嘢唔需要太强求
With a clear conscience, we don't need to make demands for it

278
00:13:28,333 --> 00:13:31,292
就系因为你行得正企得正
Yes, just because you are honest,

279
00:13:31,292 --> 00:13:34,292
个天无理由要我李家绝后嘅
Heaven will not destine us to be without descendants

280
00:13:35,958 --> 00:13:36,875
大师
Master

281
00:13:38,292 --> 00:13:39,125
大师
Master

282
00:13:40,833 --> 00:13:42,333
左右两边系十八罗汉
The eighteen Lo Hans are on both sides

283
00:13:42,333 --> 00:13:43,375
降龙伏虎系嗰边
Dragon and Tiger Fighters on this side

284
00:13:43,375 --> 00:13:44,167
求子呢就梗系⋯
To ask for a son…

285
00:13:44,167 --> 00:13:46,750
大师，头先啲嘢你讲过啦　　啊，再见⋯
- Master, you said just now    - Goodbye…

286
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:47,792
我哋仲未拜神呀
We haven't prayed to the gods yet

287
00:13:47,792 --> 00:13:49,208
拜神⋯
Pray…

288
00:14:07,458 --> 00:14:08,917
哦？降龙罗汉？
Dragon Fighter Lo Han?

289
00:14:09,208 --> 00:14:10,750
大师，我哋想⋯
Master, we want…

290
00:14:12,333 --> 00:14:13,917
我记得，要生仔呀嘛
I remember. You want a son, right?

291
00:14:15,708 --> 00:14:17,250
无问题
No problem

292
00:14:17,250 --> 00:14:20,083
又会陀咗十八个月都仲未出生嘅
Hasn't been a delivery even after 18 months’ pregnancy

293
00:14:20,083 --> 00:14:21,708
你唔驶咁担心嘅夫人
Don't worry, madam

294
00:14:21,708 --> 00:14:23,667
老爷，夫人，你睇吓
Master, madam, look

295
00:14:26,167 --> 00:14:28,250
喺边度摘㗎？　　呢⋯嗰度啰
- Where did you pluck it?    - Over there

296
00:14:30,708 --> 00:14:33,625
老爷呀，点解会咁㗎？　　老爷，夫人
- Master, why?    - Master, madam

297
00:14:34,292 --> 00:14:35,500
以前有显贵嘅人诞生
Whenever a noble is born,

298
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:37,125
就会有灵芝异像嘅出现
Ling Tze plant will appear

299
00:14:37,125 --> 00:14:38,250
但而家咁样睇嚟
From the way things look,

300
00:14:38,250 --> 00:14:39,708
咁我哋呢位未出生嘅少爷
our future young master

301
00:14:39,708 --> 00:14:40,875
一定系贵人嚟㗎啦
must be a dignitary

302
00:14:40,917 --> 00:14:42,333
而家搞到成间屋都系冬菇
The house is now full of mushrooms

303
00:14:42,333 --> 00:14:43,792
夫人，呢个仔⋯
Madam, this child…

304
00:14:43,792 --> 00:14:46,875
你自己同佢讲啦，佢而家出紧嚟啦
Tell him yourself, he's coming out

305
00:14:51,917 --> 00:14:53,958
恭喜呀老爷，夫人生咗啦
Congratulations, master! Madam has given birth

306
00:14:53,958 --> 00:14:54,667
仔定女呀？
A son or a daughter?

307
00:14:54,667 --> 00:14:57,458
仔嚟㗎，恭喜呀老爷　　恭喜呀老爷⋯
- A son! Congratulations, master    - Congratulations, master…

308
00:15:01,542 --> 00:15:03,583
喂⋯点解会降咗落嚟呢处呀？
Hey… why have we landed here?

309
00:15:03,583 --> 00:15:04,792
呢度咩地方呀？
What's this place?

310
00:15:04,792 --> 00:15:05,708
街啰
The main street

311
00:15:05,708 --> 00:15:07,917
街？仆你臭街个街呀？
Main street? Damn you

312
00:15:07,917 --> 00:15:10,167
我叫你带我去降龙投胎嗰度吖嘛
I asked you to take me to Dragon Fighter's birthplace

313
00:15:10,167 --> 00:15:11,708
行过几条咪系啰
Just a few streets further

314
00:15:11,708 --> 00:15:13,000
咁都会降落错嘅真系
How could you land in the wrong place

315
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,708
鬼叫你正话郁嚟郁去咩
Who asked you to rock so much

316
00:15:14,917 --> 00:15:15,875
个仔去咗边度呀？
Where's our son?

317
00:15:15,875 --> 00:15:16,833
我都唔知㖞
I don't know either

318
00:15:16,833 --> 00:15:19,208
哎呀⋯仆街⋯真系好痛⋯真系⋯
Aiya… damn… it's really painful… really…

319
00:15:20,042 --> 00:15:22,458
冚家富贵，嗰间死人铺头
Damn, everyone got diarrhea

320
00:15:22,458 --> 00:15:24,917
食完出嚟，个个都肚痛
after eating at that restaurant

321
00:15:24,917 --> 00:15:26,417
唏⋯顶　　顶
- Damn it    - Damn it

322
00:15:26,875 --> 00:15:29,250
求吓你啦，借个茅厕俾我哋用一用
Could we please use your manure pit?

323
00:15:29,250 --> 00:15:30,333
十万火急　　系呀⋯
- It's urgent    - Yes…

324
00:15:30,333 --> 00:15:31,542
我哋得两格茅厕咋
We only have two

325
00:15:31,542 --> 00:15:32,292
随便啦
Help yourself

326
00:15:32,333 --> 00:15:34,125
唏哟⋯忍无可忍啦
I can't hold on

327
00:15:34,125 --> 00:15:35,792
咁冇风度㗎　　咁就走咗去
- So graceless    - They run so swiftly

328
00:15:35,792 --> 00:15:37,167
我就嚟濑啦
I can hardly hold on

329
00:15:37,875 --> 00:15:38,875
系呢处啦嘛？
So this is the right place?

330
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:39,833
唏⋯降龙
Dragon Fighter

331
00:15:41,333 --> 00:15:43,667
哗⋯大佬，等你好耐啦，大佬
Brother, I waited for ages, brother

332
00:15:43,792 --> 00:15:44,708
唔关我事呀
Not my fault!

333
00:15:44,708 --> 00:15:47,000
骑呢怪啰，带住我左兜右兜咁
This bastard misled me

334
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,208
唔好讲咁多，攞番把扇先嘞，嚟⋯
Never mind, take your fan, here…

335
00:15:48,208 --> 00:15:50,583
快啲攞嚟啦　　喂⋯龙⋯
- Quick and give them to me    - Hey… Lung…

336
00:15:50,583 --> 00:15:51,958
叫你买两只蟋蟀都买咁耐嘅
What took you ages to buy 2 crickets?

337
00:15:51,958 --> 00:15:54,208
唏呀，拣两只至好打吖嘛　　懒叻吖
- I hand-picked two that fight best    - Brag

338
00:15:54,208 --> 00:15:56,792
龙⋯死嘞，佢直情睇我唔到㖞
Lung… Oh God! He can't see me

339
00:15:56,792 --> 00:15:58,125
佢已经系凡人嚟㗎啦
He is a layman now.

340
00:15:58,125 --> 00:15:58,917
想同佢接触呀
To contact him,

341
00:15:58,917 --> 00:16:00,292
你要转世投胎变成肉身
you must re-incarnate and become human

342
00:16:00,292 --> 00:16:02,250
佢都牛高马大，投胎都离唔切啦
He's now grown; too late for re-incarnation I guess

343
00:16:02,250 --> 00:16:04,000
上面一日咋，凡间就十年㗎啦
A day in Heaven is ten years in the mortal world

344
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,333
不过唔驶惊，我可以吹大你㗎
Don't worry! I'll blow you up

345
00:16:05,667 --> 00:16:06,500
吹大我？
Blow me up?

346
00:16:06,500 --> 00:16:07,083
不过吹大你
But you'll lose your magic powers

347
00:16:07,083 --> 00:16:08,500
以后呢你啲法力就会冇晒
after blowing up,

348
00:16:08,500 --> 00:16:10,167
上番天嗰阵呢，就变成白痴
and you'll become a moron when back to Heaven

349
00:16:10,167 --> 00:16:11,417
咁咪系啰，变咗白痴
Then it'll be no use contacting him

350
00:16:11,417 --> 00:16:12,792
同佢接触到都无用啦
if I become a moron

351
00:16:12,792 --> 00:16:15,125
