884
00:39:34,167 --> 00:39:35,542
点解唔叫你阿妈去祭呀？
Why don't you send your mother?

885
00:39:35,542 --> 00:39:38,167
系呀，禽晚你唔系同我讲好憎你老婆
That's right You told me you hated your wife last night

886
00:39:38,167 --> 00:39:39,292
你唔绑佢？
Why don't you send her?

887
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:41,125
我知道天爷咁样做系好难做嘅
Master Tin, I know it's a hard decision for you

888
00:39:41,125 --> 00:39:43,167
乜嘢难做？呢度冚唪呤都系我啲人
Why? They are all mine

889
00:39:43,167 --> 00:39:44,750
我要佢生就生，要佢死就死
Their lives are in my hands

890
00:39:44,750 --> 00:39:45,375
系咪？
Right?

891
00:39:45,375 --> 00:39:47,083
系呀⋯
That's right…

892
00:39:47,083 --> 00:39:49,667
嗰几个成日都冇人叫嘅，同我搞掂佢
Take those ones who nobody wants

893
00:39:49,833 --> 00:39:51,375
悭番啲米饭
I can save some costs

894
00:39:52,042 --> 00:39:54,167
啊⋯唔驶咁多，一个半个就够啦
No need for so many, one is more than enough

895
00:39:54,167 --> 00:39:57,208
出嚟围个圈，围个圈　　好衰㗎⋯
- Come and form a circle…    - So bad…

896
00:39:58,208 --> 00:40:01,750
快啲⋯爽手啲啦，埋嚟⋯　　激死人⋯
- Hurry… Quick! Come…    - Outrageous…

897
00:40:03,083 --> 00:40:04,542
驼背佬，瞓低
Hunchback, lie down

898
00:40:10,458 --> 00:40:11,875
只脚指向边个，边个中
Whoever his toe points to, will be the one

899
00:40:13,500 --> 00:40:16,458
转啦⋯转呀转⋯　　好惊呀⋯
- Turn…    - So scary…

900
00:40:30,458 --> 00:40:32,875
哦⋯你奸猾
You're cheating

901
00:40:36,333 --> 00:40:37,500
呀⋯唔系我⋯
Not me…

902
00:40:37,583 --> 00:40:38,333
拉佢去祭坛
Take her away

903
00:40:38,333 --> 00:40:39,958
唔系我呀，你哋都见到啦
Not me! You've seen it

904
00:40:39,958 --> 00:40:41,083
行呀　　拉佢
- Get going    - Take her away

905
00:40:41,083 --> 00:40:43,000
你记唔记得你禽晚讲过啲咩啫？
Remember what you said to me yesterday?

906
00:40:43,042 --> 00:40:45,208
话你收得贵啰，行啦
I said you charged a high price. Move

907
00:40:45,250 --> 00:40:46,292
唔好讲咁多，拉佢去啦
Cut the crap, take her away

908
00:40:47,917 --> 00:40:49,625
系我怡香院发烂渣？
You dare create trouble here?

909
00:40:51,167 --> 00:40:56,583
唔系呀，唔系⋯唔系我呀⋯
No! No… Not me…

910
00:40:56,583 --> 00:40:58,708
哎呀⋯喂，点祭法？
Hey, how should the sacrifice be offered?

911
00:40:58,708 --> 00:40:59,375
红烧
Braise

912
00:40:59,375 --> 00:41:02,083
咁就有排啦　　唔系我呀⋯
- It'll take a long time then    - Not me…

913
00:41:02,083 --> 00:41:04,292
留番只左腿俾我，等我抖番阵
Leave the left leg for me I'll take a rest

914
00:41:04,625 --> 00:41:06,792
捉佢沐浴更衣，行
Clean her up and get changed. Go

915
00:41:06,875 --> 00:41:08,167
唔好呀⋯
No…

916
00:41:20,958 --> 00:41:24,167
哗，咁靓，烧咗佢𠻀啲㖞
She's so beautiful. What a waste to burn her?

917
00:41:25,208 --> 00:41:26,292
想办法救佢啦
Find a way to save her

918
00:41:26,833 --> 00:41:27,833
靓至救呀？
To help only the pretty one?

919
00:41:27,875 --> 00:41:29,208
咁烧你就唔驶救啦系嘛？
If so, I won't save you then

920
00:41:33,292 --> 00:41:35,917
你⋯你把扇真系要等天光先有法力呀？
Your… your fan has to wait until dawn for its power to return?

921
00:41:36,833 --> 00:41:37,875
与其等天光
Rather than wait until dawn,

922
00:41:37,875 --> 00:41:39,583
不如等我啲法力消失好过啦
better off to wait till my powers are gone

923
00:41:39,792 --> 00:41:40,792
行
Go

924
00:41:40,958 --> 00:41:41,917
嗱我解释你听你就明㗎嘞
You'll understand once I explain to you

925
00:41:41,917 --> 00:41:44,583
唔使嘞，你点讲我都唔明㗎嘞
No need. I don't understand anyway

926
00:41:44,583 --> 00:41:46,000
唉，咁你照我说话做啦
Just do as I say

927
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,625
时辰到
The auspicious time has come

928
00:41:50,583 --> 00:41:52,292
咪住，借问声
Wait! How you know that

929
00:41:52,292 --> 00:41:54,875
你点知道烧咗佢就会冇瘟疫呢？
burning her will stop the plague?

930
00:41:55,750 --> 00:41:59,083
因为玉帝托梦话我知嘅　　哦⋯
- Heavenly Highness told me in a dream    - Oh…

931
00:42:02,667 --> 00:42:07,208
皇母娘娘头先托梦话我知
Queen Mother told me to burn…

932
00:42:09,083 --> 00:42:13,167
话烧⋯你老母　　唔系吖话⋯
- …your mother in a dream    - It can't be…

933
00:42:13,667 --> 00:42:16,042
仲话闹你三声呢
And if I scold you three times,

934
00:42:16,042 --> 00:42:19,708
你块面上面嗰两挞黑嘢就会冇咗嘞
the two moles on your face will disappear

935
00:42:19,875 --> 00:42:21,250
你痴线嘅，躙开
You are crazy, go away

936
00:42:21,500 --> 00:42:22,750
啱时候嘞，闹佢
It's time, scold him

937
00:42:23,292 --> 00:42:24,208
我唔够胆
I dare not

938
00:42:27,333 --> 00:42:29,125
契弟，契弟，正契弟
Bastard, bastard, bastard

939
00:42:31,125 --> 00:42:34,500
哗⋯真系好灵呀⋯
It really works…

940
00:42:34,542 --> 00:42:37,875
嗱⋯你哋睇吓佢块面真系仲灵过神仙吖
Look at his face, more divine than god

941
00:42:37,875 --> 00:42:40,417
各位，佢已经同皇母娘娘讲掂数
Everyone, he has made an agreement with Queen Mother,

942
00:42:40,417 --> 00:42:41,792
以后唔会再有瘟疫㗎嘞
there'll be no more plague

943
00:42:42,042 --> 00:42:43,125
即刻放人
Release her now

944
00:42:43,708 --> 00:42:46,042
若然放咗佢，仲有瘟疫，咁点先？
What if there'll be plague again after she is released?

945
00:42:46,333 --> 00:42:47,167
系咪呀⋯
Right…

946
00:42:48,583 --> 00:42:50,417
你话点嘞⋯吓？你话⋯
What to do? Tell me…

947
00:42:50,417 --> 00:42:52,167
唔关我事呀，唔好呀，唔知
None of my business! Don't! I don't know

948
00:42:53,833 --> 00:42:54,500
冇得放吖
Can't release her

949
00:42:54,500 --> 00:42:57,458
但之系咁㖞，若然烧死佢都仲有瘟疫
However, if the plague still persists after she's burnt to death

950
00:42:57,458 --> 00:42:58,917
就要烧埋你哋
I'll burn you all

951
00:43:00,375 --> 00:43:03,458
嗱，听唔听到吖？仲唔放人？
Hear that? Release her now

952
00:43:03,833 --> 00:43:05,250
烧到扑，点放吖？
The fire is so fierce. How to release?

953
00:43:05,250 --> 00:43:06,417
揾水嚟淋熄佢啦嘛
Bring some water to put it out

954
00:43:06,417 --> 00:43:09,083
唉⋯街口个井封咗，边度有水呀？
The well nearby is blocked. Where can we find water?

955
00:43:10,333 --> 00:43:13,125
冇井水啫，求其乜水都好，攞嚟啦
Any kind of water will do

956
00:43:13,292 --> 00:43:14,542
哦⋯明白
Got it

957
00:43:21,292 --> 00:43:23,292
哗⋯你咁勇，避都唔避吓
You're so bold, you don't even flinch

958
00:43:23,333 --> 00:43:25,542
吓？口水嚟之嘛，怕咩呀？
It's just saliva, no need to be scared

959
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:13,083
唔该晒
Thank you

960
00:44:14,375 --> 00:44:15,750
应该嘅
My pleasure

961
00:44:16,583 --> 00:44:18,500
我⋯
I…

962
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:36,292
你抖吓先啦吓
Take a rest

963
00:44:36,458 --> 00:44:39,500
唉⋯你唔好走啦
Don't go

964
00:44:40,333 --> 00:44:43,917
放心啦，嗰啲人唔会再嚟烧你㗎嘞
Don't worry, they won't burn you again

965
00:44:44,208 --> 00:44:46,750
班衰佬吖，平日喺床上对我咁好
Those lousy men were nice to me when in bed

966
00:44:47,583 --> 00:44:49,542
点解要用火烧死我㖞
Why did they want to burn me to death?

967
00:44:49,792 --> 00:44:52,458
个原因系咁嘅，啲人嚟揾你
It's simple Those men who come to you,

968
00:44:52,458 --> 00:44:54,042
就好似坐马桶一样
treat you like a shit-bowl

969
00:44:54,042 --> 00:44:56,833
坐紧嘅时候，固然之系好畅快啦
They feel comfortable when sitting on it,

970
00:44:56,833 --> 00:44:59,875
但系段唔会对个马桶产生感情
but they're not emotionally tied to it

971
00:45:00,750 --> 00:45:01,833
咁即系点呀？
What do you mean?

972
00:45:01,833 --> 00:45:05,625
即系⋯叫你以后唔好再做马桶，明吗？
That is… to say, never be a shit-bowl anymore Get it?

973
00:45:06,250 --> 00:45:07,042
我明
Yes

974
00:45:08,458 --> 00:45:09,583
做咩呀⋯吓？
What are you doing?

975
00:45:09,583 --> 00:45:10,542
我报答你啰
I want to repay you

976
00:45:10,542 --> 00:45:13,417
咪啦你，真是鸡性难改
Don't! Your whorish nature is incorrigible

977
00:45:13,417 --> 00:45:14,667
我唔收你嘅钱㗎㖞
It's free

978
00:45:14,667 --> 00:45:16,292
哗⋯大佬，你唔收钱之㖞
Big brother, you don't charge,

979
00:45:16,292 --> 00:45:17,167
我收㖞
but I do

980
00:45:17,208 --> 00:45:18,125
仲衰过个马桶
Worse than a shit-bowl

981
00:45:18,333 --> 00:45:20,625
你除咗晓瞓低收钱之外仲晓做啲咩呀？
What else can you do besides lying down for money?

982
00:45:23,917 --> 00:45:26,833
倒吊都得？唔系呀话⋯
You can do it upside down? No way…

983
00:45:27,708 --> 00:45:29,208
唔系同你讲呢啲呀
I don't mean that

984
00:45:29,375 --> 00:45:31,167
我系话，你可唔可以，揾过第二份嘢做
What I mean is can you find another job…

985
00:45:31,167 --> 00:45:33,333
譬如话，卖吓豆腐，咁得唔得啫？
…like selling bean curd?

986
00:45:34,083 --> 00:45:35,875
个档口摆喺门口定系床边呀？
Should I put the stall at the door or beside the bed?

987
00:45:42,375 --> 00:45:45,458
师父⋯乞到半砖腐乳呀
Master… I got half a piece of preserved bean curd

988
00:45:47,625 --> 00:45:50,125
嗄⋯好香呀，系咪有我份呀？
Smells good, any for me?

989
00:45:50,500 --> 00:45:51,583
腐乳就有你份
Keep the bean curd for yourself

990
00:45:52,292 --> 00:45:55,417
唔系呀，喂汁都饮埋呀
Oh no, finish the sauce too

991
00:45:57,125 --> 00:45:58,958
番狗嚟啫，冇乜味嘅
It's a foreign dog, not much taste

992
00:45:58,958 --> 00:46:00,458
仲有嚿呀，试过至知
There's one left. Try and I'll know

993
00:46:01,292 --> 00:46:02,708
呢只狗生前咬死过两个人
This dog has bitten two people to death before

994
00:46:02,708 --> 00:46:04,250
家吓我食佢系超渡紧佢咋
Eating it means I'm honoring its dead spirit

995
00:46:04,250 --> 00:46:06,083
你又想嗒，仲未够班呀
You're not qualified yet to eat it

996
00:46:06,167 --> 00:46:06,958
唔系呀师父
Not really, Master.

997
00:46:06,958 --> 00:46:08,958
狗肉穿肠过，徒弟好肚饿呀⋯
Your pupil is very hungry

998
00:46:15,750 --> 00:46:18,042
拍硬档，留番嚿骨嚟嘬吓
Be kind enough to leave me at least a piece of bone

999
00:46:18,667 --> 00:46:21,542
嚟呀⋯拍硬档呀⋯嚟呀⋯
Please… be kind… please…

1000
00:46:21,958 --> 00:46:23,042
过主呀
Go away

1001
00:46:23,250 --> 00:46:26,375
做吓好心呀，喂，咁都唔得呀，喂
Be kind! Hey! Why not? Hey

1002
00:46:26,375 --> 00:46:29,042
嗱⋯，唔好玩嘞，我知你未吞呀
Don't play! I know you haven't swallowed it

1003
00:46:29,500 --> 00:46:30,250
我顶你条仆街
You bastard,

1004
00:46:30,250 --> 00:46:31,917
第二样唔见你咁有斗志
how come you ain't that persistent apart from begging?

1005
00:46:31,917 --> 00:46:33,125
帮帮忙啦⋯嚟呀⋯
Help… C'mon…

1006
00:46:37,375 --> 00:46:39,167
我要摆档㗎
I need to get the rack.

1007
00:46:41,083 --> 00:46:42,208
记得攞番条底裤呀
Remember to get back your underpants

1008
00:46:42,208 --> 00:46:43,333
攞咗啦
Get it

1009
00:46:44,417 --> 00:46:46,250
乜咁耐㗎？到我啦
Why took so long? It's my turn.

1010
00:46:46,250 --> 00:46:47,000
入嚟啦
Come

1011
00:46:47,000 --> 00:46:47,958
玉
Yuk

1012
00:46:48,750 --> 00:46:49,792
乜系你呀？
It's you

1013
00:46:49,875 --> 00:46:53,250
你唔听我说话不特止，家吓仲变本加厉
You aren't listening to me and get even worse now

1014
00:46:53,250 --> 00:46:54,708
实在太唔自爱
You have no self-respect at all

1015
00:46:54,708 --> 00:46:56,458
我照足你吩咐去做㗎
I've done as you told me

1016
00:46:57,000 --> 00:46:59,500
你做鸡做到小贩咁样，通街摆档
You are simply hawking yourself in the street

1017
00:46:59,500 --> 00:47:02,292
好意思话照足我吩咐嘅
How dare you say you're doing as I said

1018
00:47:02,667 --> 00:47:05,292
错嘞，我卖紧豆腐㗎⋯
Wrong! I'm selling bean curd…

1019
00:47:10,875 --> 00:47:12,583
喳⋯真系卖豆腐？
Really?

1020
00:47:13,458 --> 00:47:15,333
喂，快啲啦，系咪唔做生意㗎？
Hurry up, are you doing business or not?

1021
00:47:15,333 --> 00:47:17,083
话明买碗豆腐灼一镬㗎嘛
We agreed to do once for buying a bowl of bean curd

1022
00:47:17,167 --> 00:47:18,208
唔做吖？攞番钱嚟啰⋯
No? Give me back the money…

1023
00:47:18,208 --> 00:47:20,417
唔系呀⋯做吖⋯嚟吖⋯
No… I'll do it… Coming…

1024
00:47:22,083 --> 00:47:23,542
多谢你嘅提点吖
Thanks for your advice

1025
00:47:23,542 --> 00:47:25,167
家吓啲生意做都做唔切呀
My business is good now

1026
00:47:27,875 --> 00:47:30,250
佢肯改嘅，系用错方法嘅啫
She's willing to change, just in the wrong way

1027
00:47:30,250 --> 00:47:31,333
大种，跟我来
Dai Jung, follow me

1028
00:47:34,958 --> 00:47:37,958
喂⋯帮帮忙⋯我有少少请求
Hey… help… Please do me a favor

1029
00:47:38,083 --> 00:47:39,792
千其唔好喺呢条街附近呢
Don't mention my nickname here. Thanks

1030
00:47:39,792 --> 00:47:41,875
用头先个名叫我，唔该
my nick name here. Thanks

1031
00:47:42,417 --> 00:47:43,333
我叫你咩名？
What did I call you?

1032
00:47:45,500 --> 00:47:46,708
大种乞儿
Beggar Dai Jung

1033
00:47:46,875 --> 00:47:48,125
你个名叫大种乞儿？
Is your name Beggar Dai Jung?

1034
00:47:48,167 --> 00:47:49,417
你个名叫周溢祥嘛⋯死⋯
Your name is Chow Yat Cheung… Go to hell…

1035
00:47:49,417 --> 00:47:50,208
唔好打啦⋯
Don't beat me…

1036
00:47:50,208 --> 00:47:51,917
如果你要打呢，我带你去后巷
If you want to beat me, let's go to the back alley

1037
00:47:51,917 --> 00:47:54,250
任打，呢度会俾小玉见到
Beat freely. Siu Yuk will see us here

1038
00:47:54,250 --> 00:47:55,375
我带你去
I'll show you the way

1039
00:47:56,667 --> 00:47:59,583
呵⋯原来要喺小玉面前
So your pride will only appear

1040
00:47:59,583 --> 00:48:02,292
你嘅自尊心先会蒲头吖
in the presence of Siu Yuk

1041
00:48:03,042 --> 00:48:04,125
我明嘞
I got it

1042
00:48:04,208 --> 00:48:05,708
明嘞
Got it

1043
00:48:06,625 --> 00:48:08,458
边个话佢哋冇得救，系人都有得救
Who says they have no remedy? They all have remedy

1044
00:48:08,458 --> 00:48:12,125
上面你班友听住，呢镬我赢硬呀
Listen, fairies above, I'll surely win

1045
00:48:36,667 --> 00:48:40,417
喺呢个世上，除咗佢我边个都唔嫁
I won't marry any man except him in this world

1046
00:48:54,917 --> 00:48:57,083
曳呀你，装人冲凉
You're naughty, you peeping-tom

1047
00:48:57,583 --> 00:48:59,500
好衰㗎，唔准讲人哋㗎吓
Bad boy, I forbid you to say this

1048
00:49:03,292 --> 00:49:04,750
就系呢个造型
This is the style

1049
00:49:05,292 --> 00:49:08,500
一个好女子，就应该系咁样
A decent girl should be like this

1050
00:49:12,667 --> 00:49:15,042
都唔痛嘅？我都知系发紧梦㗎啦
Not hurt? I know it's a dream

1051
00:49:15,042 --> 00:49:16,417
唔系点会变成咁吖
Or else this couldn't have happened

1052
00:49:16,833 --> 00:49:17,958
得嘅
You can

1053
00:49:22,667 --> 00:49:26,208
咩虫嚟㗎？咁肉酸嘅⋯咦⋯
What's it? So ugly…

1054
00:49:27,625 --> 00:49:28,542
你睇
Look

1055
00:49:29,333 --> 00:49:30,875
好靓呀⋯
So beautiful…

1056
00:49:31,417 --> 00:49:34,458
玉，既然毛虫可以变蝴蝶
Yuk, since a caterpillar can become a butterfly,

1057
00:49:34,750 --> 00:49:37,125
咁鸡⋯都一样可以变凤凰
a chicken… can also become a phoenix

1058
00:49:37,333 --> 00:49:39,167
我又要做凤凰，得唔得吖？
I want to be a phoenix, can I?

1059
00:49:49,250 --> 00:49:50,292
凤凰？
A phoenix?

1060
00:50:04,625 --> 00:50:07,583
主宫，你真系有先知之明
Lord, you have good foresight

1061
00:50:08,542 --> 00:50:11,500
个和尚所做嘅一切，正如你所讲
That monk has done all that you anticipated

1062
00:50:12,250 --> 00:50:14,333
你有咩吩咐，即管讲
If you need anything, just tell me

1063
00:50:15,458 --> 00:50:16,542
（怡香院）
(Yi Heung Brothel)

1064
00:50:18,375 --> 00:50:20,125
叫鸡？第日先啦
Call a whore? Maybe another day

1065
00:50:22,083 --> 00:50:23,250
唔得闲呢
I have no time

1066
00:50:24,833 --> 00:50:26,833
哎呀我推你得啫，你推我⋯过嚟
I can push you, but you push me back… come here

1067
00:50:27,417 --> 00:50:28,625
嗱⋯唔好打吖
Don't hit me

1068
00:50:28,625 --> 00:50:30,250
屎又屙咗，凉又唔洗冲
You've gone to the toilet, and you don't need a bath

1069
00:50:30,250 --> 00:50:31,292
你仲有咩嘢做？
What else do you need to do?

1070
00:50:31,292 --> 00:50:33,625
系啫，但系叫鸡⋯唔识吖嘛
But calling a whore… I don't know how

1071
00:50:33,625 --> 00:50:35,875
小玉喺上面等紧佢嘅心上人
Siu Yuk is waiting for her lover upstairs

1072
00:50:36,583 --> 00:50:37,708
边个？
Who is it?

1073
00:50:37,833 --> 00:50:40,583
佢叫做⋯周溢祥
His name is… Chow Yat Cheung

1074
00:50:40,875 --> 00:50:41,958
我？
Me?

1075
00:50:43,333 --> 00:50:45,708
一个风度翩翩嘅靓仔
A good-looking and presentable man

1076
00:51:01,542 --> 00:51:02,667
Yeah⋯
Yeah…

1077
00:51:04,125 --> 00:51:07,625
大种，你记住初更一响就一定要松人
Dai Jung, you must remember to leave on the 1st watch

1078
00:51:07,625 --> 00:51:10,375
若然唔系，黄金会变返狗屎
Otherwise, gold will turn back to dog shit,

1079
00:51:10,375 --> 00:51:12,375
大孖疮都会标番晒出嚟
and the sores will emerge again

1080
00:51:12,375 --> 00:51:14,083
咁吓亲人就冇谓
It'd be bad to scare people away

1081
00:51:21,125 --> 00:51:22,375
有冇相熟小姐呀？
Do you have any familiar lady in mind?

1082
00:51:22,375 --> 00:51:23,208
小玉
Siu Yuk

1083
00:51:23,208 --> 00:51:24,250
佢姨妈嚟㖞
She is having her period

1084
00:51:26,375 --> 00:51:27,667
佢姨妈好疏堂嘅啫
Her period has just ended

1085
00:51:27,667 --> 00:51:29,250
不过佢喺度搭住，唔接客㗎
She's only a temporary lodger here, not taking any client

1086
00:51:30,250 --> 00:51:32,333
哎呀⋯唔紧要
Never mind,

1087
00:51:32,333 --> 00:51:33,708
佢耐唔中都要客串下嘅
she sometimes makes guest appearances

1088
00:51:33,708 --> 00:51:35,167
公子，跟我嚟啦
Sir, follow me

1089
00:51:40,667 --> 00:51:41,542
小玉
Siu Yuk

1090
00:51:42,125 --> 00:51:43,208
叫我凤凰吖
Call me Phoenix

1091
00:51:45,250 --> 00:51:47,083
官人，不如我吩咐厨房
Sir, how about I order the kitchen to cook

1092
00:51:47,083 --> 00:51:48,667
整几味小菜你食先啦
some dishes for you?

1093
00:51:48,958 --> 00:51:50,208
唔知你钟意食咩呢？
What would you like?

1094
00:51:50,750 --> 00:51:53,375
如果有成钵鸡屎忽呢，咁就正啦
A plate of chicken butts would be nice

1095
00:51:54,500 --> 00:51:55,833
冇咩唔妥吖嘛？
Anything wrong?

1096
00:51:56,125 --> 00:51:57,000
识货
You're an epicure

1097
00:52:02,708 --> 00:52:03,792
做盛行吖？
What do you do?

1098
00:52:04,000 --> 00:52:06,292
乞儿　　哦？
- I'm a beggar    - What?

1099
00:52:07,208 --> 00:52:08,833
原来系你
So it's you

1100
00:52:09,167 --> 00:52:10,625
你唔会嫌弃我吖嘛？
Do you mind?

1101
00:52:11,250 --> 00:52:14,250
点会呢？我见到你就好似见到阿边个咁
Why would I? When I see you it's like seeing that guy

1102
00:52:14,250 --> 00:52:15,125
呀边个呢？
Where's that guy?

1103
00:52:15,125 --> 00:52:16,417
呀边个叫我嚟揾你
That guy asked me to come

1104
00:52:16,417 --> 00:52:17,917
呀边个叫你嚟揾我做咩事呀？
Why did he ask you to come?

1105
00:52:17,917 --> 00:52:19,917
呀边个叫我嚟揾你⋯
That guy asked me here to…

1106
00:52:21,125 --> 00:52:22,375
⋯买豆腐
…buy bean curd

1107
00:52:22,625 --> 00:52:24,375
咦⋯好衰㗎
You're so naughty

1108
00:52:33,583 --> 00:52:35,542
啱晒，顺便搅掂埋你
Good! I'll fix you too

1109
00:52:43,625 --> 00:52:46,333
有少林祖师达摩上身，一盏灯时间
With the possession of Shaolin Patriarch Dharma, in a lamp’s time,

1110
00:52:46,333 --> 00:52:48,083
冇理由搅你唔掂啩
there's no reason I can't fix you

1111
00:52:48,542 --> 00:52:49,500
企喺度
Halt

1112
00:52:49,792 --> 00:52:50,333
郁佢
Sock him

1113
00:52:50,333 --> 00:52:50,875
系
Yes

1114
00:52:57,208 --> 00:53:01,500
咩事呀⋯，睇吓⋯咩事呀⋯
What happened… Look… what happened?

1115
00:53:02,292 --> 00:53:03,417
果然有料到
Really powerful

1116
00:53:04,042 --> 00:53:05,250
达摩？
Patriarch Dharma?

1117
00:53:06,792 --> 00:53:07,958
惊呢麻甩佬
Are you scared?

1118
00:53:07,958 --> 00:53:10,708
我睇你个样，作恶太多，罪孽深重
You are deep in sin

1119
00:53:10,708 --> 00:53:11,792
我当系做吓善事
Consider this as doing charity,

1120
00:53:11,792 --> 00:53:13,500
带你返去做和尚洗底
I'll take you back to be a monk

1121
00:53:13,500 --> 00:53:14,500
去你老母
Damn you

1122
00:53:15,333 --> 00:53:16,875
打到你去
I'll beat you till you come with me

1123
00:53:20,333 --> 00:53:22,167
开玩笑呀⋯藤条
Joking… A rattan cane

1124
00:53:24,292 --> 00:53:25,417
睇少我系话
Look down on me?

1125
00:53:25,417 --> 00:53:26,500
怕未？
Scared now?

1126
00:53:27,417 --> 00:53:28,833
唉⋯好攰
I'm tired

1127
00:53:31,500 --> 00:53:34,125
呀⋯，走呀⋯
Go…

1128
00:53:37,750 --> 00:53:38,708
走去边？
See where you can run to?

1129
00:53:42,833 --> 00:53:44,625
冚家富贵，教极唔听系话
Damn it! Never listen

1130
00:54:31,708 --> 00:54:34,458
服未？　　服你老味
- Reconciled to defeat yet?    - Reconciled to the hell of you

1131
00:54:45,500 --> 00:54:47,083
呀⋯原来呀边个系神仙嚟㗎
So, that guy is a fairy?

1132
00:54:47,083 --> 00:54:48,917
嗄⋯乜你唔知嘅咩？
I thought you knew

1133
00:54:48,917 --> 00:54:51,042
嗳⋯唔好意思呀，要你咁辛苦
Sorry for troubling you

1134
00:54:51,042 --> 00:54:52,250
冇伤肝，我钟意嘅⋯
Never mind. I enjoy it…

1135
00:54:52,750 --> 00:54:53,583
要几多砖呀？
How many?

1136
00:54:53,583 --> 00:54:55,125
咁嘅情形，要两砖够嘞
For a situation like this, two will suffice

1137
00:54:56,417 --> 00:54:58,042
记得同呀边个讲
Remember to tell that guy I'll sell soy milk

1138
00:54:58,042 --> 00:54:59,833
我听日卖埋豆浆㗎
as well tomorrow

1139
00:54:59,833 --> 00:55:00,750
系？
Really?

1140
00:55:01,125 --> 00:55:03,625
你估呀边个钟意食咸定甜吖嗱
Do you think he'll like it salty or sweet?

1141
00:55:03,625 --> 00:55:04,375
咸嘅
Salty

1142
00:55:04,375 --> 00:55:05,667
落啲榨菜好㖞
Best to add some preserved savory vegetables

1143
00:55:05,792 --> 00:55:07,083
落啲芝麻仲香
Even better with sesame seeds

1144
00:55:07,458 --> 00:55:09,333
罗汉斋豆浆
Lo Han soy milk

1145
00:55:09,333 --> 00:55:10,500
佢钟意食狗肉㗎
He likes dog meat

1146
00:55:10,500 --> 00:55:12,833
狗肉罗汉斋豆浆
Dog meat Lo Han soy milk

1147
00:55:13,625 --> 00:55:15,250
Yeah⋯
Yeah…

1148
00:55:17,833 --> 00:55:20,000
小玉无敌豆浆霸
Siu Yuk's unbeatable soy milk

1149
00:55:20,000 --> 00:55:21,000
Yeah⋯
Yeah…

1150
00:55:21,000 --> 00:55:23,917
哎呀⋯我嚟叫鸡㗎幡
I've come for a whore

1151
00:55:32,917 --> 00:55:34,833
既然系咁，我唯有以暴易暴
As matters stand, I have to fight violence with violence

1152
00:55:36,750 --> 00:55:37,833
铁头功
Iron Head

1153
00:55:49,875 --> 00:55:51,125
认输未呀？
Reconciled to defeat now?

1154
00:55:51,708 --> 00:55:54,042
而家叫你做和尚啫又唔系叫你去死
I only want you to be a monk, not go to hell

1155
00:55:54,042 --> 00:55:55,417
即刻乖乖哋跟我返去
Be good and come with me now

1156
00:56:00,417 --> 00:56:02,458
真系冥顽不灵⋯哼
You're simply incorrigible

1157
00:56:05,917 --> 00:56:07,583
算嘞⋯，唔做和尚就罢就嘞
OK… forget about being a monk

1158
00:56:07,583 --> 00:56:09,167
总之以后唔好再杀人，得嘞啩
Just refrain from killing people, okay?

1159
00:56:16,125 --> 00:56:18,958
仆你个街吖，究竟系人定系野兽？
Damn! Are you a human being or a beast?

1160
00:56:26,708 --> 00:56:27,750
钟唔钟意我呀？
Do you like me?

1161
00:56:27,750 --> 00:56:28,375
钟意
I do

1162
00:56:28,375 --> 00:56:29,417
不过，下世先啦
But, make it next life

1163
00:56:29,500 --> 00:56:32,458
今世，我一定要嫁俾阿边个先甘心嘅
This life, I have to marry that guy

1164
00:56:32,458 --> 00:56:33,958
咁又系嘅，我都系识咗佢之后
You're right. I found my self-respect

1165
00:56:33,958 --> 00:56:35,500
先发觉自己有自尊
after knowing him too

1166
00:56:41,792 --> 00:56:43,417
今晚当我买你怕
OK, you're on the upside tonight

1167
00:56:43,417 --> 00:56:44,708
嗱一人行一步吖嗱
Let's compromise! If you back off

1168
00:56:44,708 --> 00:56:45,833
只要你今日唔上去搅亚玉
and leave Siu Yuk alone tonight,

1169
00:56:45,833 --> 00:56:47,458
我同你笔账就第二日至算啦
we'll settle our score later

1170
00:56:55,417 --> 00:56:58,375
哗⋯如果我唔系变咗身咪俾你对死咗
If I hadn't changed to Patriarch Dharma, I'd have been killed by you

1171
00:56:58,625 --> 00:57:00,083
你个死铲吖
You bastard

1172
00:57:00,750 --> 00:57:02,417
忍无可忍嘞
Can't bear with it anymore

1173
00:57:14,292 --> 00:57:16,833
我佛慈悲，大吉大利
Buddha is merciful! Good luck

1174
00:57:27,000 --> 00:57:30,708
币家伙，大种，时辰到喇
Shit! Dai Jung, it's time

1175
00:57:32,417 --> 00:57:33,708
边个卖粽呀？
Is someone selling rice dumplings?

1176
00:57:33,833 --> 00:57:34,750
嗰档嘢日日都喺度㗎
That stand's there every day.

1177
00:57:34,750 --> 00:57:35,875
唔洗理佢㗎　　哦
- Never mind it    - OK

1178
00:57:38,625 --> 00:57:41,667
啲法术用完晒啦，走啦⋯
Magic is over! Let's go

1179
00:57:42,250 --> 00:57:44,250
仆街嘞，时辰到
Shit! Time is up

1180
00:57:46,667 --> 00:57:48,500
哎呀⋯我变番咁样呀
Aiya… I changed back to a beggar

1181
00:57:48,500 --> 00:57:50,750
哎呀咩啫，你系乞儿嚟㗎嘛
Why shout? You are in fact a beggar

1182
00:57:51,708 --> 00:57:52,875
我要走嘞
I have to go

1183
00:57:53,250 --> 00:57:56,083
喂，我哋系好朋友呵？
Hey, are we good friends?

1184
00:57:58,625 --> 00:58:00,083
唉⋯仲唔落嚟⋯你真系⋯
Why haven't you come down yet… you really…

1185
00:58:00,083 --> 00:58:00,958
靓仔
Hey man

1186
00:58:02,042 --> 00:58:04,167
见唔见嗰个，满面胡须嘅亚差呀？
Have you seen someone with a big beard?

1187
00:58:04,625 --> 00:58:06,583
有呀，好似走咗去茅厕嗰边
Yes, he seems over there in the toilet

1188
00:58:07,000 --> 00:58:07,792
追
After him

1189
00:58:08,583 --> 00:58:09,542
企喺度
Halt

1190
00:58:10,167 --> 00:58:11,542
靓仔，好熟面口㖞
Man, you look familiar

1191
00:58:12,750 --> 00:58:14,875
两位壮士，怕认错人嘞
Heroes, you're mistaken

1192
00:58:20,917 --> 00:58:21,875
岂有此理
Outrageous!

1193
00:58:21,875 --> 00:58:23,583
叫咗你唔好俾我见到你㗎啦
I warned you not to let me see you

1194
00:58:23,583 --> 00:58:24,667
唔好呀⋯
Don't…

1195
00:58:25,083 --> 00:58:26,292
仲叫霸王鸡？
Sponge as well?

1196
00:58:26,583 --> 00:58:28,875
唔系呀，我冇叫霸王鸡呀
No, I didn't

1197
00:58:28,875 --> 00:58:30,250
我有钱㗎
I have money

1198
00:58:30,917 --> 00:58:32,292
死嘞，黄金变⋯
Shit! The gold changed…

1199
00:58:40,333 --> 00:58:42,875
你唔好打佢啦，佢唔系叫霸王鸡呀
Don't beat him! He's not a sponger

1200
00:58:43,333 --> 00:58:44,458
佢系我条仔嚟㗎
He's my boyfriend

1201
00:58:44,458 --> 00:58:46,542
咁贱？生疮你都要？
That cheap? You even want one with sores?

1202
00:58:49,167 --> 00:58:50,125
睇嘢呀
Look

1203
00:58:51,167 --> 00:58:52,792
喂大佬呀，都话唔系我啰
Big brother, I told you it wasn't me

1204
00:58:52,792 --> 00:58:53,708
你仲唔认？
You still deny it?

1205
00:58:53,708 --> 00:58:55,458
洗乜咁劳气呀？人有相似啫
Don't be mad! Maybe it's just likeness

1206
00:58:55,458 --> 00:58:56,833
你分明喺度扮鬼扮马
You're pretending

1207
00:58:56,833 --> 00:58:58,167
我似个满面胡须嗰亚差咩？
Do I look like that moustached Singh?

1208
00:58:58,167 --> 00:58:58,875
剃咗佢唔得呀？
Maybe you shaved it off?

1209
00:58:58,875 --> 00:59:00,417
剃须边有剃得咁快呀
Who could do it so quickly?

1210
00:59:00,417 --> 00:59:02,042
唉呀⋯你即系帮外人嚟窒我啫
You're siding with a stranger

1211
00:59:02,042 --> 00:59:03,083
我讲道理咋噃
I talk sense

1212
00:59:03,083 --> 00:59:04,000
死啦
Go to hell

1213
00:59:05,708 --> 00:59:06,750
嗱⋯系咪呢，而家打亲人嘞
See! You've hurt someone

1214
00:59:06,750 --> 00:59:07,542
咩呀？发烂渣呀？
What? Getting mad?

1215
00:59:07,542 --> 00:59:09,042
咩呀？唔通企喺度俾你打呀？
What? Should I stand here and let you hit me?

1216
00:59:09,167 --> 00:59:09,875
咩呀？连大佬嘅说话都唔听呀？
What? You dare disobey what the big brother tells you to do?

1217
00:59:09,875 --> 00:59:10,583
咩呀？以大恰细呀
What? A big one bullies a small one?

1218
00:59:10,625 --> 00:59:11,750
我忍你好耐嘞　　去死啦
- I've endured for a long time.    - Go to hell

1219
00:59:11,750 --> 00:59:15,458
唔好打我大佬呀，行开
Don't beat my big brother! Go away

1220
00:59:15,458 --> 00:59:19,167
仆街啦，哗⋯又嚟，唔好呀⋯喂⋯
Damn it! Again! Don't… Hey…

1221
00:59:19,292 --> 00:59:20,500
唔好呀
Don't

1222
00:59:20,500 --> 00:59:21,375
救命呀
Help

1223
00:59:21,375 --> 00:59:22,708
唔好呀大爷
Don't, master

1224
00:59:23,125 --> 00:59:24,250
放过佢啦大爷
Let her go, please, master

1225
00:59:29,583 --> 00:59:30,542
小玉⋯
Siu Yuk…

1226
00:59:34,125 --> 00:59:36,792
救命呀
Help

1227
00:59:38,250 --> 00:59:40,083
大嚿衰
Big head

1228
00:59:44,667 --> 00:59:45,875
大种
Dai Jung

1229
00:59:47,333 --> 00:59:48,667
做咩入嚟唔敲门呀？
Why didn't you knock?

1230
00:59:48,958 --> 00:59:49,917
对唔住揾错
Sorry, I got the wrong place

1231
00:59:50,125 --> 00:59:51,250
顺手闩门呀
Close the door

1232
00:59:51,792 --> 00:59:52,500
食蕉呀
Have a banana

1233
00:59:52,583 --> 00:59:53,750
对唔住⋯
Sorry…

1234
00:59:56,333 --> 00:59:57,625
师父⋯
Master…

1235
00:59:58,125 --> 00:59:59,625
唉⋯咁耐都唔落嚟，作死咩？
What's taken you so long? Wanna die?

1236
00:59:59,625 --> 01:00:00,875
打回原形嘞，嗱嗱声走啦
Things changed back to the original! Let's go

1237
01:00:00,875 --> 01:00:02,833
师父，我走唔到呀
Master, I can't move

1238
01:00:11,542 --> 01:00:13,292
吓？袁霸天
What? Yun Ba Tin

1239
01:00:19,292 --> 01:00:20,958
去死啦，大种乞儿
Go to hell, Beggar Dai Jung

1240
01:00:25,667 --> 01:00:26,833
唔好再叫我大种
Don't call me Dai Jung

1241
01:00:27,417 --> 01:00:29,375
我叫周溢祥
Call me Chow Yat Cheung

1242
01:00:35,958 --> 01:00:36,917
大种
Dai Jung

1243
01:00:38,500 --> 01:00:39,583
你都害得我哋惨啦
You've made us suffer a lot

1244
01:00:39,583 --> 01:00:41,125
大种⋯你唔好死住呀大种
Dai Jung… you can't die!

1245
01:00:41,125 --> 01:00:41,792
你顶多阵呀
You must hang on

1246
01:00:41,792 --> 01:00:43,583
大种⋯你唔死得㗎，大种
Dai Jung… you can't die! Dai Jung

1247
01:00:43,583 --> 01:00:45,125
你冇晒法术呢
You've no more magical powers?

1248
01:00:45,125 --> 01:00:47,000
听日有，听日你就知死
Tomorrow, I'll show you tomorrow

1249
01:00:54,208 --> 01:00:55,500
杀你个冚家铲
Kill you, son of a bitch

1250
01:00:55,708 --> 01:00:58,458
拧佢块面过嚟　　拧番块面呀
- Turn his face over    - Turn his face

1251
01:01:00,250 --> 01:01:01,208
睇呀
Look

1252
01:01:10,167 --> 01:01:11,542
掹开佢对眼
Open his eyes

1253
01:01:17,792 --> 01:01:21,042
哼，天爷话放你一马，醒定啲呀
Master Tin said to let you go, but be careful in future

1254
01:01:21,042 --> 01:01:22,750
头先益晒你啦，睇到眼都唔眨
What a show it was just now You didn't even blink

1255
01:01:22,833 --> 01:01:24,125
吓⋯讲真又几精彩㖞
Frankly… it was fascinating

1256
01:01:24,125 --> 01:01:25,083
系啰
Yes

1257
01:01:28,792 --> 01:01:32,500
哈⋯呢次你仲唔死？
You'll surely die this time

1258
01:01:34,708 --> 01:01:35,667
土地
God of Earth

1259
01:01:37,375 --> 01:01:41,458
土地，你喺边呀？快啲出嚟呀⋯
God of Earth, where are you? Come out quickly

1260
01:01:43,250 --> 01:01:46,500
喂⋯咪嚟咗啰，咁大声做咩呀？
Hey… I'm here. Why shouting so loud?

1261
01:01:46,500 --> 01:01:48,042
点样先至可以救番大种乞儿？
How can I save Dai Jung?

1262
01:01:48,333 --> 01:01:52,250
人嘅生死早有定数天条规矩冇得变
A man's fate is pre-determined One can't change Heaven's rules

1263
01:01:52,250 --> 01:01:53,458
但佢系为我冤枉死嘅
But he has suffered an innocent death because of me

1264
01:01:53,458 --> 01:01:54,792
无论如何都要掹番佢上嚟
I've got to bring him back no matter what

1265
01:01:54,792 --> 01:01:56,042
你快啲同我谂谂办法啦
Help me to think of some ways

1266
01:01:56,042 --> 01:01:57,750
枉死就实落地狱
An innocent death means going to hell

1267
01:01:58,500 --> 01:02:00,750
阎王份人，冇偈倾
King of Hades is strict

1268
01:02:01,083 --> 01:02:02,083
不过⋯
But…

1269
01:02:02,500 --> 01:02:03,500
讲啦
Speak up

1270
01:02:03,708 --> 01:02:05,833
入枉死城之前
Before entering the City of Innocent Deaths,

1271
01:02:05,833 --> 01:02:08,375
有一段系邪神黑罗刹嘅地头
There's an area governed by evil god Hak Lo Sat

1272
01:02:08,917 --> 01:02:10,917
佢专门收埋啲游魂野鬼
He admits stray spirits

1273
01:02:11,417 --> 01:02:13,708
落喺佢手，就永不超生
Anyone in his hands never gets reincarnated

1274
01:02:14,333 --> 01:02:16,333
不过，佢就有偈倾
But you may talk it over with him

1275
01:02:16,333 --> 01:02:17,625
咁你快啲带我落去见佢呀
Bring me down to him quickly

1276
01:02:17,625 --> 01:02:21,125
喂⋯我系普通料嚟咋仲未有资格落去
Hey… I'm only a junior god and thus not eligible to go down

1277
01:02:21,125 --> 01:02:23,875
唔同你呀，你有金身护住
Unlike you, you've a golden body for protection

1278
01:02:23,875 --> 01:02:25,625
可以上上落落都冇问题
which makes you invulnerable

1279
01:02:26,542 --> 01:02:27,875
咁我即刻返去攞个金身
I'll go and get the golden body back now

1280
01:02:27,875 --> 01:02:30,958
喂⋯你唔好攞个金身嚟较飞呀
Hey… don't make fun of the golden body

1281
01:02:30,958 --> 01:02:32,042
唔得都要得㗎嘞
I must do what's necessary

1282
01:02:38,083 --> 01:02:39,083
做咩呀？放手
What're you doing? Let go

1283
01:02:39,083 --> 01:02:41,000
师父话个金身唔可以离开间寺㗎
Master said this golden body cannot leave the temple

1284
01:02:41,000 --> 01:02:43,333
妖⋯若然离开又如何？
What if it does?

1285
01:02:43,333 --> 01:02:44,417
唔知　　咁即系冇事啦
- I don't know    - Then that means it's okay

1286
01:02:44,417 --> 01:02:46,167
借嚟用一用，你最多起钉啫
Let me borrow it, I'll pay you lots of interest

1287
01:02:46,542 --> 01:02:47,792
唔得　　一晚咁多呢
- No    - For just one night

1288
01:02:47,792 --> 01:02:48,750
唔得　　一个时辰呢
- No    - One hour

1289
01:02:48,750 --> 01:02:50,167
唔得　　咁就大字形㗎啦㖞
- No    - OK, then a cross

1290
01:02:50,167 --> 01:02:51,667
唔得　咩大字型？
What cross?

1291
01:03:49,375 --> 01:03:50,417
喂靓仔你咪郁
Hey man, halt

1292
01:03:50,417 --> 01:03:51,500
企定
Stand still

1293
01:03:51,833 --> 01:03:52,875
咩事？
What's the matter?

1294
01:03:54,125 --> 01:03:55,000
放咗佢
Let him go

1295
01:03:55,042 --> 01:03:56,958
哼，你系如来佛祖呀？
Are you the Buddha?

1296
01:03:56,958 --> 01:03:57,542
唔系
No

1297
01:03:57,542 --> 01:03:58,333
挑
Damn

1298
01:04:07,375 --> 01:04:09,958
靓仔，你好冇礼貌吓，我讲你听
Man, you're so rude. Let me tell you

1299
01:04:09,958 --> 01:04:11,208
我同佛祖系老死嚟
I'm friends with the Buddha

1300
01:04:11,500 --> 01:04:13,500
家吓我代表佢攞番呢个人嘅三魂七魄
I'll retrieve this person's spirit on his behalf,

1301
01:04:13,500 --> 01:04:14,542
清楚唔清楚呀？
understand?

1302
01:04:16,875 --> 01:04:18,250
你够胆？咪嚟呀
How dare you? Stop

1303
01:04:18,250 --> 01:04:19,042
咪嚟呀
Stop

1304
01:04:31,792 --> 01:04:34,292
正垃圾，叫释迦牟尼嚟见我啦
Rubbish! Ask Sakyamuni to see me

1305
01:04:35,958 --> 01:04:37,583
唔好走住呀⋯
Don't go…

1306
01:04:38,083 --> 01:04:40,542
其实，我同阿佛祖都唔系好熟㗎啫
In fact, I'm not on good terms with Buddha

1307
01:04:40,917 --> 01:04:42,917
我又唔知你同佢有牙齿痕㗎嘛
I didn't know you and he had a grudge

1308
01:04:43,500 --> 01:04:44,750
当我叫声你大佬
I'll take you for big brother

1309
01:04:44,750 --> 01:04:47,458
你横是咁多靓，多件唔多，少件唔少
Since you've so many men under you, having one more doesn't make a difference

1310
01:04:47,458 --> 01:04:49,667
嗰件⋯当醒俾我呢
This one… treat this as a gift to me

1311
01:04:49,667 --> 01:04:51,875
我醒俾你有咩着数呀？
What's in it for me?

1312
01:04:51,875 --> 01:04:52,792
着数？
What's in it?

1313
01:04:53,500 --> 01:04:56,375
一系⋯我帮你修修啲脚甲佢呀咁长
How about… I'll pedicure for you, the nails are so long,

1314
01:04:56,375 --> 01:04:57,208
好吗？
okay?

1315
01:04:57,458 --> 01:05:01,583
挑，除非你攞个金身嚟交换啦，哼
Damn! Unless you exchange it with your golden body

1316
01:05:01,917 --> 01:05:04,292
金身？我个金身唔俾得你㗎㖞
Golden body? I can't give it to you

1317
01:05:04,292 --> 01:05:05,667
况且你要嚟都冇用㗎
Besides, you've no use for it

1318
01:05:06,083 --> 01:05:07,250
摆吓都好㗎
Just as a display

1319
01:05:07,250 --> 01:05:09,417
哗⋯冚家铲，你咁抵死嘅你
Bastard, you're going too far

1320
01:05:09,417 --> 01:05:11,167
好，我换
Okay, exchange

1321
01:05:14,125 --> 01:05:16,208
大种，点都带你返去
Dai Jung, I must bring you back by any means

1322
01:05:16,583 --> 01:05:17,417
你定呀
Don't worry

1323
01:05:17,417 --> 01:05:18,708
放低你个金身
Put down your golden body

1324
01:05:44,500 --> 01:05:45,875
你应承同我交换㗎㖞
You promised to exchange with me

1325
01:05:45,875 --> 01:05:47,375
你做咩吸走佢嘅魂魄呀？
Why have you taken his spirit?

1326
01:05:47,375 --> 01:05:48,792
我奸㗎嘛
I'm a baddie

1327
01:06:02,625 --> 01:06:05,292
臭和尚，失惊无神咁飞出嚟
Stinking monk, why appeared so sudden

1328
01:06:05,292 --> 01:06:06,875
哎呀，死火啦，返番上嚟添
Damn, I'm back

1329
01:06:06,875 --> 01:06:08,917
你唔钟意呀，咪返番落去啰
If you don't like it, you can go back down

1330
01:06:08,917 --> 01:06:11,042
我冇咗个金身，我想返番落去都唔得呀
How could I go down without the golden body?

1331
01:06:11,292 --> 01:06:12,667
呢镬冇阴公呀呢镬
What a pity!

1332
01:06:12,667 --> 01:06:13,917
连个金身都俾人呃埋
He's even cheated me out of my golden body

1333
01:06:14,417 --> 01:06:15,875
大种⋯
Dai Jung…

1334
01:06:16,417 --> 01:06:18,042
大种⋯
Dai Jung…

1335
01:06:21,958 --> 01:06:23,208
大种⋯
Dai Jung…

1336
01:07:03,833 --> 01:07:07,000
主宫，我一定照你嘅吩咐
Lord, I'll do as you instruct me

1337
01:07:07,750 --> 01:07:09,583
帮你完成你嘅大业
and help accomplish your mission

1338
01:07:22,833 --> 01:07:26,583
喂⋯唔系咁吖嘛
Hey… don't be like that?

1339
01:07:26,583 --> 01:07:27,875
喂⋯兄弟
Hey… brothers…

1340
01:07:29,417 --> 01:07:30,917
一啲面都唔俾？
Won't give me a face?

1341
01:07:31,292 --> 01:07:33,125
我话晒都系嚟度嘅陀哋㖞
I'm in charge here

1342
01:07:34,958 --> 01:07:36,208
我都话咗呢单嘢济唔过㗎啦
I told you not to do this

1343
01:07:36,208 --> 01:07:37,292
咩事啫究竟？
What's the matter?

1344
01:07:37,708 --> 01:07:39,458
入面嗰班神仙
As you have consorted with evil spirits,

1345
01:07:39,458 --> 01:07:41,667
佢哋话你同邪魔打交道
the fairies inside said…

1346
01:07:41,667 --> 01:07:43,667
个个都唔肯同你埋堆呀
…they don't want to be with you

1347
01:07:43,875 --> 01:07:47,292
冚唪呤走晒，呢班友返嚟执行李㗎咋
They've all gone These just returned to get their luggage.

1348
01:07:47,417 --> 01:07:49,583
对唔住嘞，我就嚟咬长粮
Sorry, for my life-long emoluments,

1349
01:07:49,583 --> 01:07:51,583
焗住跟大队啦⋯系咁先啦
I have to follow them… goodbye

1350
01:08:03,125 --> 01:08:06,542
吓？乜搅成咁呀？啲嘢呢？
What's happening? Where's the stuff?

1351
01:08:07,625 --> 01:08:09,042
济癫，个金身呢？
Mad Monk, where's the golden body?

1352
01:08:11,208 --> 01:08:13,333
你死嘞，搅个祸出嚟啦
Oh no! You've caused big trouble

1353
01:08:17,042 --> 01:08:19,083
哎呀惨喇，连土地都唔见埋添
Oh no! Even God of Earth is gone.

1354
01:08:19,083 --> 01:08:20,167
今次闯祸嘞
We're in deep shit now

1355
01:08:20,208 --> 01:08:21,750
哎呀，惨喇⋯
Oh no…

1356
01:08:38,833 --> 01:08:40,250
师父，你去边呀？
Master, where are you going?

1357
01:08:40,500 --> 01:08:42,417
济癫，我都话咗㗎啦
Mad Monk, as I told you,

1358
01:08:42,417 --> 01:08:44,417
个金身唔可以离开间寺㗎
the golden body cannot leave the temple

1359
01:08:44,417 --> 01:08:46,333
而家搞到神憎鬼厌
Now you've caused anger among men and gods

1360
01:08:46,333 --> 01:08:48,292
你叫我点担当得起呀？
how can I bear this responsibility?

1361
01:08:49,042 --> 01:08:50,208
师父，快啲走啦
Master, leave quickly

1362
01:08:50,208 --> 01:08:52,583
话唔定一个雷劈落嚟，将间庙擘冧呀
Thunder may split the temple

1363
01:09:00,083 --> 01:09:02,833
连你都怪我？　　走啦⋯连观音都冧咗啦
- You blame me too?    - Let's go… even the Goddess is down.

1364
01:09:02,917 --> 01:09:03,667
走啦⋯
Go…

1365
01:09:03,917 --> 01:09:04,875
还原
Back to original form

1366
01:09:11,375 --> 01:09:13,542
真系赶到我咁绝？
You really leave me no way out?

1367
01:09:18,583 --> 01:09:21,917
喂小玉，听讲你寻日俾天爷玩到残晒㖞
Siu Yuk, I heard you were messed up by Master Tin last night

1368
01:09:21,917 --> 01:09:23,083
系咪真㗎？
Is that true?

1369
01:09:24,042 --> 01:09:26,167
唓⋯唔睬人㗎，好巴闭咩？
Ignoring us! What's so special?

1370
01:09:26,167 --> 01:09:27,833
都残晒啦，揾小红好过啦
You're rotten. We'll look for Siu Hung

1371
01:09:27,875 --> 01:09:29,000
等一阵呀
Wait

1372
01:09:30,042 --> 01:09:31,792
点呀？小玉姐
What's the matter, Miss Siu Yuk?

1373
01:09:31,792 --> 01:09:33,000
我唔收钱，你济？
If I don't charge you money, would you take me?

1374
01:09:33,417 --> 01:09:34,750
济，喂，咁即刻嚟啰
Yes, do it now

1375
01:09:34,750 --> 01:09:35,708
我都济呀
Me too

1376
01:09:35,833 --> 01:09:36,958
喂⋯佢嗌我先㗎㖞
Hey… She asked me first

1377
01:09:36,958 --> 01:09:37,583
我先呀⋯　　我先㗎㖞⋯
- Me first…    - Me first…

1378
01:09:37,583 --> 01:09:38,500
几时轮到你哋？
Who says it's your turn?

1379
01:09:38,500 --> 01:09:39,458
我先㗎⋯　　我先⋯
- Me first…    - Me first…

1380
01:09:53,917 --> 01:09:56,875
你话我听，你要点至开心？
Tell me, what will make you happy?

1381
01:09:57,000 --> 01:09:58,000
嫁俾你呀
Marrying you

1382
01:09:58,000 --> 01:09:59,083
你曳呀你
You're naughty

1383
01:09:59,333 --> 01:10:00,500
嫁俾你呀
Marrying you

1384
01:10:00,708 --> 01:10:02,958
咁系咪嫁咗俾我，你就唔再做鸡先？
If I marry you, will you stop being a whore?

1385
01:10:02,958 --> 01:10:03,750
唔做嘞
Yes

1386
01:10:03,750 --> 01:10:04,625
系咪呀？
Really?

1387
01:10:04,875 --> 01:10:06,000
梗系啦
Yes

1388
01:10:06,000 --> 01:10:06,917
娶你
We'll marry then

1389
01:10:12,292 --> 01:10:15,500
我降龙罗汉，法号济癫和尚
I am Dragon Fighter Lo Han, priest name Mad Monk

1390
01:10:15,500 --> 01:10:17,292
今日愿娶白小玉为妻
I'll take Bak Siu Yuk as my wife today

1391
01:10:17,417 --> 01:10:20,000
无论佢前世种种，今生各样
Whatever comes in this life or came in the past life,

1392
01:10:20,417 --> 01:10:21,917
此誓永不言悔
I'll not regret it

1393
01:10:27,917 --> 01:10:30,167
但系我一双玉臂千人枕
Even I've been pillowed

1394
01:10:30,167 --> 01:10:32,083
半点朱唇万客尝
and kissed by thousands of people,

1395
01:10:32,083 --> 01:10:32,667
你都⋯
you still…

1396
01:10:32,667 --> 01:10:34,042
唔紧要，顶得住
Never mind, I can take it

1397
01:10:34,042 --> 01:10:35,375
Yeah⋯
Yeah…

1398
01:10:35,958 --> 01:10:37,083
你真系咁爱我？
You really love me?

1399
01:10:37,583 --> 01:10:38,958
我好爱你
I love you very much

1400
01:10:39,417 --> 01:10:40,792
你爱我有几深呀？
How deep is your love?

1401
01:10:41,750 --> 01:10:43,375
就好似爱大种乞儿一样
As deep as I love Beggar Dai Jung

1402
01:10:46,292 --> 01:10:47,333
大种乞儿？
Beggar Dai Jung?

1403
01:10:48,750 --> 01:10:49,917
你爱边个多啲呀？
Who do you love more?

1404
01:10:49,917 --> 01:10:50,917
一样
The same

1405
01:10:52,333 --> 01:10:54,625
吓得我吖，我几惊你爱佢多啲呀
Scared me! I thought you loved him more

1406
01:10:54,625 --> 01:10:55,833
唔系⋯一样
No… the same

1407
01:10:55,833 --> 01:10:57,417
Yeah⋯
Yeah…

1408
01:10:59,333 --> 01:11:00,458
点解你唔开心嘅？
Yeah… why are you not happy?

1409
01:11:00,458 --> 01:11:02,750
喔⋯唔系⋯ Yeah ⋯
No… Yeah…

1410
01:11:02,750 --> 01:11:04,375
好呀，拜堂呀
Great… Let's worship the ancestors

1411
01:11:04,375 --> 01:11:05,167
好⋯嚟呀⋯
Good… go…

1412
01:11:05,167 --> 01:11:07,417
拜完堂，我哋去埋便洞房⋯
After that we'll consummate our marriage…

1413
01:11:07,417 --> 01:11:08,792
要快啲⋯　　然后生埋仔
- We must be quick…    - …then we'll have kids

1414
01:11:08,792 --> 01:11:09,958
唔系我惊赶唔切喇⋯
I'm afraid there's not enough time

1415
