Not only a failure.

1591
01:25:02,417 --> 01:25:03,500
如果当日俾我同佢只揪
If you let me beat him in a duel on that day,

1592
01:25:03,500 --> 01:25:05,833
揪赢佢就唔洗搅镬粥啦
things wouldn't have been such a mess

1593
01:25:05,833 --> 01:25:06,958
耶⋯你喺度讲嘢吖你⋯
Nonsense…

1594
01:25:06,958 --> 01:25:08,292
成日喺度话只揪
Stop mentioning the duel

1595
01:25:08,750 --> 01:25:10,958
冇错，大种乞儿系枉死
No doubt Beggar Dai Jung

1596
01:25:10,958 --> 01:25:12,250
不过佢临死前
suffered an innocent death

1597
01:25:12,250 --> 01:25:14,000
学识自己叫周溢祥
But before he died, he knew his name was Chow Yat Cheung

1598
01:25:14,000 --> 01:25:16,375
即系佢重新攞番佢嘅自尊
It means he got back his pride

1599
01:25:16,958 --> 01:25:19,625
你哋睇吓　　有嘢睇㖞⋯
- Look…    - Something to watch…

1600
01:25:19,625 --> 01:25:21,833
佢今世唔洗再做乞儿喇　　系㖞⋯
- He doesn't have to be a beggar this life    - Right…

1601
01:25:32,792 --> 01:25:35,583
至于小玉，块面虽然系花咗
Though Siu Yuk was defaced,

1602
01:25:35,583 --> 01:25:37,833
但系佢已经唔再做鸡
she's no longer a whore

1603
01:25:37,833 --> 01:25:39,792
而真真正正去卖豆腐
She's really selling bean curd now

1604
01:25:39,875 --> 01:25:41,708
无恶不作嘅袁霸天
As for the villain Yun Ba Tin

1605
01:25:41,708 --> 01:25:44,083
我哋都听到佢临死前嘅忏悔
We all know that when he died

1606
01:25:44,083 --> 01:25:45,500
系唔想再做人
he said he didn't want to be a human being anymore

1607
01:25:46,000 --> 01:25:48,750
而家佢已经转入轮回喇
He's now reincarnated

1608
01:25:49,542 --> 01:25:52,667
今世做猪啫，前途一片光明
In this life he’s a pig, he's got a bright future

1609
01:25:53,625 --> 01:25:57,458
咁大家谂谂，降龙究竟系输，定系赢？
Let us think did Dragon Fighter win or lose?

1610
01:25:57,458 --> 01:25:58,500
哦⋯
Well…

1611
01:25:58,958 --> 01:26:02,667
不过点都好，降龙罗汉已经唔再存在
No matter what, Dragon Fighter Lo Han no longer exists

1612
01:26:05,417 --> 01:26:06,250
你跌咗碌嘢吖
You've dropped something

1613
01:26:06,250 --> 01:26:07,250
好彩我同你执番咋嗱
Lucky I pick up for you

1614
01:26:07,250 --> 01:26:09,958
但系就多咗个降龙尊者
But now we have a senior Dragon Fighter

1615
01:26:13,750 --> 01:26:14,875
你点会喺度㗎⋯
Why are you here?

1616
01:26:14,875 --> 01:26:17,375
哗⋯仲做埋尊者添吖　佢都可以做尊者？
- He'll be a senior    - Could he be a senior?

1617
01:26:17,458 --> 01:26:18,917
哈哈⋯系呀
Right

1618
01:26:18,917 --> 01:26:20,500
轻轻升咗几级啫
A promotion for a few grades only

1619
01:26:23,417 --> 01:26:25,167
加冕仪式开始
The coronation ceremony begins

1620
01:27:00,667 --> 01:27:01,625
恭喜晒
Congratulations

1621
01:27:01,625 --> 01:27:03,042
多谢
Thank you

1622
01:27:22,500 --> 01:27:25,083
今日你加冕成为降龙尊者
What's your goal being made

1623
01:27:25,083 --> 01:27:26,500
有咩志愿吖？
a senior Dragon Fighter today?

1624
01:27:26,750 --> 01:27:30,167
我想成为一个和平使者向凡间宣扬爱心
I want to be an emissary of peace and be Heaven's envoy to spread love throughout the world

1625
01:27:30,208 --> 01:27:34,042
等佢哋明解只要有爱心，边度都系天堂
And let them know that with love, anywhere is a paradise.

